locked":false,"text":"This is O(following_count) index\nlookups per feed read.\n@500 followees = 500 index scans\nper request. Works fine up to\n~50K DAU, then falls apart.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b1k","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"This is O(following_count) index\nlookups per feed read.\n@500 followees = 500 index scans\nper request. Works fine up to\n~50K DAU, then falls apart.","height":87.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#6b7280","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1251566716,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":818.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":-1861,"width":236.92173767089844},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#22c55e","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b1l","backgroundColor":"#d3f9d8","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"YkoB0s9cnLn-_qunMkXB7","x":-251.5596923828125,"seed":869805252,"boundElements":[],"y":-1701,"opacity":100,"height":130,"width":740,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1366962500},{"seed":893252676,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"N2kWzj6WhUSvTybfk0Exp","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":17,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Why It Works at Low Scale","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b1m","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Why It Works at Low Scale","height":21.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#15803d","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1064269052,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":-1693,"width":225.31781005859375},{"seed":629066692,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"E_LJ7zZczL1HsCiNYMd4k","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"- Single PostgreSQL handles thousands of simple queries\/sec\n- No distributed systems complexity — deploy on 2 servers total\n- Iterate fast: entire system understandable by one engineer\n- Joins complete in <20ms when tables are small and warm in memory","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b1n","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"- Single PostgreSQL handles thousands of simple queries\/sec\n- No distributed systems complexity — deploy on 2 servers total\n- Iterate fast: entire system understandable by one engineer\n- Joins complete in <20ms when tables are small and warm in memory","height":70,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1227581636,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":-1667,"width":461.7755126953125},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#ef4444","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b1o","backgroundColor":"#ffc9c9","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"NPvsXEa8KuXC7SmUAI4FP","x":508.4403076171875,"seed":381203268,"boundElements":[],"y":-1701,"opacity":100,"height":130,"width":770,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1076852092},{"seed":659139268,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"zl_Y5PtzD9hCU0837DbeT","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":17,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Capacity Ceiling + Why It Breaks","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b1p","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Capacity Ceiling + Why It Breaks","height":21.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b91c1c","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":885633092,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":518.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":-1693,"width":271.69378662109375},{"seed":2043654724,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"USmYDwskk67zNnOOBmUV9","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Breaks above ~500 concurrent users (~50K DAU) because:\n- JOIN on follows+posts = expensive full-index scan per request\n- No caching: every read hits DB disk I\/O\n- Single writer: post writes + like writes contend on same instance\n- No async: one slow DB query blocks the API thread","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b1q","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Breaks above ~500 concurrent users (~50K DAU) because:\n- JOIN on follows+posts = expensive full-index scan per request\n- No caching: every read hits DB disk I\/O\n- Single writer: post writes + like writes contend on same instance\n- No async: one slow DB query blocks the API thread","height":87.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":438003196,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":518.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":-1667,"width":452.00338745117188},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#4a9eed","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b1r","backgroundColor":"#dbe4ff","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"Sabc87zvqc8TvEN8T3Shp","x":-251.5596923828125,"seed":757647812,"boundElements":[],"y":-1556,"opacity":100,"height":75,"width":1530,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":875759556},{"seed":1416819012,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"uLi3dUiHx4fM7EGdOxzIW","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":16,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Say to interviewer:","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b1s","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Say to interviewer:","height":20,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#2563eb","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":573916796,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":-1544,"width":146.639892578125},{"seed":1863067844,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"6e4b3PuxpBgANVBQOmwDD","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":15,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"\"I am starting with the simplest design to establish a baseline and make tradeoffs explicit. This works at startup scale but has a hard ceiling around 50K DAU.\nLet me identify exactly where it breaks before adding complexity.\"","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b1t","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"\"I am starting with the simplest design to establish a baseline and make tradeoffs explicit. This works at startup scale but has a hard ceiling around 50K DAU.\nLet me identify exactly where it breaks before adding complexity.\"","height":37.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":998600516,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":-1521,"width":1177.3193359375},{"seed":1620209732,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"egY5ZDsjY2duWyDEM30Wm","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":26,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"NEWS FEED — Step 6: Bottleneck Identification","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b1u","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"NEWS FEED — Step 6: Bottleneck Identification","height":32.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1027544828,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":98.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":-1383,"width":628.4976806640625},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#ef4444","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b1v","backgroundColor":"#ffc9c9","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":3,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"GfiwVZeDxMIfT4hokOa43","x":-251.5596923828125,"seed":1759758276,"boundElements":[],"y":-1341,"opacity":100,"height":175,"width":740,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":186574532},{"seed":471740228,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"PRpo8JCuMiaLyL00QkcdG","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":17,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"BN1 — Feed Query JOIN at Read Time  [I\/O-bound + CPU-bound]","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b1w","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"BN1 — Feed Query JOIN at Read Time  [I\/O-bound + CPU-bound]","height":21.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b91c1c","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1740298108,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":-1333,"width":554.4715576171875},{"seed":1520412356,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"IRK_fogycvtOSP0CU1gBZ","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"PostgreSQL fan-in JOIN across posts+follows at 232K QPS.\n500 followees x 232K QPS = 116M index ops\/sec needed.\nPostgreSQL ceiling: ~50K complex reads\/sec on one instance.\nThreshold: ~500 concurrent users (~50K DAU).\nRoot cause: No precomputed feed. Every read recomputes the full\nmerge from scratch. Cannot amortize work across users.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b1x","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"PostgreSQL fan-in JOIN across posts+follows at 232K QPS.\n500 followees x 232K QPS = 116M index ops\/sec needed.\nPostgreSQL ceiling: ~50K complex reads\/sec on one instance.\nThreshold: ~500 concurrent users (~50K DAU).\nRoot cause: No precomputed feed. Every read recomputes the full\nmerge from scratch. Cannot amortize work across users.","height":105,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":664628804,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":-1307,"width":450.00152587890625},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#ef4444","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b1y","backgroundColor":"#ffc9c9","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":3,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"nduK2SxBz0C8ai8NJcTiY","x":508.4403076171875,"seed":1225141828,"boundElements":[],"y":-1341,"opacity":100,"height":175,"width":770,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1038780412},{"seed":1211090372,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"B7LWJsPO533tDPUPCXiv5","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":17,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"BN2 — Single PostgreSQL Writer  [I\/O + Coordination-bound]","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b1z","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"BN2 — Single PostgreSQL Writer  [I\/O + Coordination-bound]","height":21.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b91c1c","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1373570500,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":518.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":-1333,"width":517.03753662109375},{"seed":1832545604,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"jgAKcOUvoAB7r1Kb3Ntp1","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Single writer hits ~5K TPS ceiling under like+post+follow writes.\n464K like\/sec as UPDATE posts SET likes=likes+1\n= serialized row-level lock on hot post rows.\nThreshold: ~5K writes\/sec (~10M DAU active likers).\nRoot cause: Row-level lock on a single hot row serializes ALL\nlike writes. Not shardable without app-layer changes.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b20","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Single writer hits ~5K TPS ceiling under like+post+follow writes.\n464K like\/sec as UPDATE posts SET likes=likes+1\n= serialized row-level lock on hot post rows.\nThreshold: ~5K writes\/sec (~10M DAU active likers).\nRoot cause: Row-level lock on a single hot row serializes ALL\nlike writes. Not shardable without app-layer changes.","height":105,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":63973500,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":518.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":-1307,"width":437.00946044921875},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#f59e0b","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b21","backgroundColor":"#ffd8a8","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":3,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"CwBw47JaFxNI9d_XDQwgG","x":-251.5596923828125,"seed":2038703300,"boundElements":[],"y":-1151,"opacity":100,"height":160,"width":740,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":2130816324},{"seed":1386933316,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"My6UkIvjg7zi3f88PTX2e","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":17,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"BN3 — Zero Cache Layer  [I\/O-bound]","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b22","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"BN3 — Zero Cache Layer  [I\/O-bound]","height":21.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b45309","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":757971196,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":-1143,"width":326.65472412109375},{"seed":2056045508,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"a-82Steuhc3oeP6CAC6IM","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"100% of 232K peak QPS hits PostgreSQL disk I\/O directly.\nSSD random read ceiling ~50K-100K IOPS. Need 232K min.\nThreshold: Breaks at >5K DAU — any meaningful traffic.\nRoot cause: Feeds are highly cacheable (same user sees same\nfeed for 30-60s) but we recompute from scratch every request.\nFeeds are read 100x more than they change — obvious cache target.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b23","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"100% of 232K peak QPS hits PostgreSQL disk I\/O directly.\nSSD random read ceiling ~50K-100K IOPS. Need 232K min.\nThreshold: Breaks at >5K DAU — any meaningful traffic.\nRoot cause: Feeds are highly cacheable (same user sees same\nfeed for 30-60s) but we recompute from scratch every request.\nFeeds are read 100x more than they change — obvious cache target.","height":105,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1348691140,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":-1117,"width":472.19140625},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#f59e0b","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b24","backgroundColor":"#ffd8a8","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":3,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"BAjL8ekver4Q3Ae5Yi84s","x":508.4403076171875,"seed":122137412,"boundElements":[],"y":-1151,"opacity":100,"height":160,"width":770,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1703229820},{"seed":456762052,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"PDU1_H5krs6pvcsJjhRyk","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":17,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"BN4 — Single API Server  [CPU + Network-bound]","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b25","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"BN4 — Single API Server  [CPU + Network-bound]","height":21.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b45309","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":195177540,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":518.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":-1143,"width":416.61865234375},{"seed":1560324676,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"UWJ9W_X80bhhUDhUEWI-1","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Single monolith process handles ~2-5K QPS max before\nthread pool exhaustion and GC pressure kick in.\nAt 232K peak QPS we need ~100+ API nodes.\nThreshold: ~5K QPS (~500K DAU).\nRoot cause: No load balancer, no stateless horizontal scaling.\nFeed read spikes also starve post-write threads — mixed workload\nin one process = no independent scaling.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b26","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Single monolith process handles ~2-5K QPS max before\nthread pool exhaustion and GC pressure kick in.\nAt 232K peak QPS we need ~100+ API nodes.\nThreshold: ~5K QPS (~500K DAU).\nRoot cause: No load balancer, no stateless horizontal scaling.\nFeed read spikes also starve post-write threads — mixed workload\nin one process = no independent scaling.","height":122.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":404269564,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":518.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":-1117,"width":458.2474365234375},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#ef4444","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b27","backgroundColor":"#ffc9c9","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":3,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"NX1EaTVqaYcD0kZtACW2P","x":-251.5596923828125,"seed":1870315972,"boundElements":[],"y":-976,"opacity":100,"height":170,"width":740,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":312214468},{"seed":1774577988,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"WR-Iba38HDyGPqE47F4fi","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":17,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"BN5 — Celebrity Fan-out at Read Time  [Dependency-bound]","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b28","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"BN5 — Celebrity Fan-out at Read Time  [Dependency-bound]","height":21.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b91c1c","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":2011826812,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":-968,"width":509.319580078125},{"seed":1329602756,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"VZfTm1iRJZ0AFo2HgWfM3","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"No precomputed feeds: every one of celebrity's 10M followers\nrecomputes the feed merge independently at their read time.\n10M followers x 10 opens\/day = 100M DB queries\/day per celebrity.\nThreshold: Breaks at >100K followers on any account.\nRoot cause: Work is not amortized. Fan-out-on-write does merge\nONCE at post time vs pull model repeating it 100M times\/day.\nAlso causes thundering herd: 10M users open app at 8pm simultaneously.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b29","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"No precomputed feeds: every one of celebrity's 10M followers\nrecomputes the feed merge independently at their read time.\n10M followers x 10 opens\/day = 100M DB queries\/day per celebrity.\nThreshold: Breaks at >100K followers on any account.\nRoot cause: Work is not amortized. Fan-out-on-write does merge\nONCE at post time vs pull model repeating it 100M times\/day.\nAlso causes thundering herd: 10M users open app at 8pm simultaneously.","height":122.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1533995844,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":-942,"width":492.2813720703125},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#f59e0b","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b2A","backgroundColor":"#ffd8a8","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":3,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"VMig5yK9HoO59RIOjbDrA","x":508.4403076171875,"seed":126314564,"boundElements":[],"y":-976,"opacity":100,"height":170,"width":770,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":129719036},{"seed":1450819524,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"ZkjWWbUQdt2UUrkbcDpX1","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":17,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"BN6 — Sync Media Upload in API Thread  [I\/O + Network-bound]","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b2B","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"BN6 — Sync Media Upload in API Thread  [I\/O + Network-bound]","height":21.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b45309","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1752752836,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":518.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":-968,"width":549.7965087890625},{"seed":1412769604,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"ipBc9v-HJIWxYi-ZyMWfe","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"API thread held open during full media upload to S3.\n10MB video on 5Mbps mobile = 16 seconds thread blocked.\nWith 100-thread pool: 7 concurrent video uploads starve all other traffic.\nThreshold: Breaks at 10-20 simultaneous uploads.\nRoot cause: Synchronous slow I\/O in the request hot path.\nFix: presigned S3 URLs — client uploads directly to S3,\nAPI just stores the resulting URL. Thread freed immediately.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b2C","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"API thread held open during full media upload to S3.\n10MB video on 5Mbps mobile = 16 seconds thread blocked.\nWith 100-thread pool: 7 concurrent video uploads starve all other traffic.\nThreshold: Breaks at 10-20 simultaneous uploads.\nRoot cause: Synchronous slow I\/O in the request hot path.\nFix: presigned S3 URLs — client uploads directly to S3,\nAPI just stores the resulting URL. Thread freed immediately.","height":122.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":571382652,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":518.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":-942,"width":501.8154296875},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#8b5cf6","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b2D","backgroundColor":"#d0bfff","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":3,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"7NwcuW1fFEhb4b0s-iYEC","x":-251.5596923828125,"seed":1696046788,"boundElements":[],"y":-791,"opacity":100,"height":150,"width":1530,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1079503428},{"seed":834610756,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"-lmFs0SjVqfvuqmesKnfY","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":17,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"BN7 — No Workload Isolation: All Traffic Competes on One DB  [State-bound + Coordination-bound]","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b2E","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"BN7 — No Workload Isolation: All Traffic Competes on One DB  [State-bound + Coordination-bound]","height":21.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#5b21b6","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":19254268,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":-783,"width":837.48724365234375},{"seed":520732100,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"BBsP9BVTQIJDadCTIDAmR","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Follow\/unfollow queries, feed reads, like writes, post writes all compete for same PostgreSQL connection pool (100-200 conns)\nand same disk I\/O budget. A viral post causing like spikes starves feed read connections entirely.\nUnfollow needs strong consistency (must read primary) but competes with eventual-ok feed reads on same instance.\nThreshold: Visible at ~50K DAU. Critical at ~500K DAU.\nRoot cause: Different workloads need different infrastructure — OLTP writes, graph traversal, and cache-population\nhave completely different access patterns. One DB cannot serve all optimally.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b2F","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Follow\/unfollow queries, feed reads, like writes, post writes all compete for same PostgreSQL connection pool (100-200 conns)\nand same disk I\/O budget. A viral post causing like spikes starves feed read connections entirely.\nUnfollow needs strong consistency (must read primary) but competes with eventual-ok feed reads on same instance.\nThreshold: Visible at ~50K DAU. Critical at ~500K DAU.\nRoot cause: Different workloads need different infrastructure — OLTP writes, graph traversal, and cache-population\nhave completely different access patterns. One DB cannot serve all optimally.","height":105,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1709834692,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":-757,"width":867.8448486328125},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#4a9eed","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b2G","backgroundColor":"#1e1e2e","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"DfHHZdSbI-r4X8fJlfU8c","x":-251.5596923828125,"seed":1175807300,"boundElements":[],"y":-623,"opacity":100,"height":88,"width":1530,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1191373948},{"seed":1816140996,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"3AExsR5PuC9p3qmapY-dE","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":17,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Fix Priority Order (Step 7 will address these one by one):","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b2H","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Fix Priority Order (Step 7 will address these one by one):","height":21.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#a5d8ff","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1347234116,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":-613,"width":479.60357666015625},{"seed":206