d":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Mechanism: Feed stored as Redis sorted set keyed by user_id, score = post timestamp. Feed read hits Redis first.\nCache miss (cold user) falls back to DB query and populates cache. DB now handles only cache misses and writes.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b2X","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Mechanism: Feed stored as Redis sorted set keyed by user_id, score = post timestamp. Feed read hits Redis first.\nCache miss (cold user) falls back to DB query and populates cache. DB now handles only cache misses and writes.","height":35,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#374151","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1096590660,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":-113,"width":787.73687744140625},{"seed":246733892,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"wM0KNMTojDYrAibolqTwh","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"New tradeoff: Fan-out writes are now synchronous in the API thread — posting to 500 followers means 500 Redis writes inline.\nCelebrity post (10M followers) = 10M Redis writes synchronously. Blocks the API thread for seconds.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b2Y","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"New tradeoff: Fan-out writes are now synchronous in the API thread — posting to 500 followers means 500 Redis writes inline.\nCelebrity post (10M followers) = 10M Redis writes synchronously. Blocks the API thread for seconds.","height":35,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b45309","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":203309308,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":-73,"width":879.84283447265625},{"seed":2144908228,"strokeSt