 (post_created topic). On post creation, API publishes ONE event to Kafka and returns 200 to client immediately.\nFan-out worker pool (150 nodes) consumes from Kafka, looks up follower list, and writes to each follower's Redis feed cache.","height":35,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1799852668,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":47,"width":928.9686279296875},{"seed":1188565188,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"VSV4-NyT77F68t5vUHnrs","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Mechanism: Post creation is now O(1) from API perspective. Fan-out work is fully async and horizontally scalable.\nWorkers partitioned by post author user_id — same author's posts always handled by same worker partition (ordering guarantee).","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b2f","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Mechanism: Post creation is now O(1) from API perspective. Fan-out work is fully async and horizontally scalable.\nWorkers partitioned by post author user_id — same author's posts always handled by same worker partition (ordering guarantee).","height":35,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#374151","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":2089673540,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":87,"width":890.2308349609375},{"seed":648108100,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"xQP-nhZLNJnhsKVfY6G2b","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"New tradeoff: Feed propagation is now eventually consistent. Follower may not see new post for up to 5-30 seconds\n(depending on Kafka consumer lag). Fan-out lag becomes a key metric to monitor.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b2g","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"New tradeoff: Feed propagation is now eventually consistent. Follower may not see new post for up to 5-30 seconds\n(depending on Kafka consumer lag). Fan-out lag becomes a key metric to monitor.","height":35,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b45309","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1177019132,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":127,"width":800.12701416015625},{"seed":1557508036,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"yE6JKQkTweKM_pLs72ibM","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":16,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Scale ceiling: ~10M DAU","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b2h","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Scale ceiling: ~10M DAU","height":20,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b91c1c","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":2063129284,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":828.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":2,"width":182.31985473632812},{"seed":160634692,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"bT1zV7_lMqmVthJA8l7_t","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"New failure: Kafka consumer lag\nbuilds up under traffic spike —\nfollowers see delayed feed.\nDLQ needed for poison pills.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b2i","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"New failure: Kafka consumer lag\nbuilds up under traffic spike —\nfollowers see delayed feed.\nDLQ needed for poison pills.","height":70,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#6b7280","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1906975612,"te