cked":false,"text":"Fixes: BN5 at mega-scale (>1M follower accounts break fan-out workers)","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b30","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Fixes: BN5 at mega-scale (>1M follower accounts break fan-out workers)","height":17.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#ef4444","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":197105660,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":577,"width":496.57949829101562},{"seed":167224772,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"a6mVFUURVOKEdXmFT4hhO","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Changed: Fan-out workers check follower count on post creation. If author has <1M followers: fan-out-on-write (push to caches).\nIf author has >1M followers (celebrity): skip fan-out. Store post in celebrity_posts table only.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b31","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Changed: Fan-out workers check follower count on post creation. If author has <1M followers: fan-out-on-write (push to caches).\nIf author has >1M followers (celebrity): skip fan-out. Store post in celebrity_posts table only.","height":35,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1134753220,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":597,"width":888.73297119140625},{"seed":1795575108,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"MmNfXvXjtkOLLQJLVURYq","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"At read time: Feed service fetches user's precomputed cache AND queries celebrity_posts for all celebrities they follow,\nmerges results by score (timestamp + ranking), returns unified feed. Merge adds ~10-20ms to read path.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b32","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"At read time: Feed service fetches user's precomputed cache AND queries celebrity_posts for all celebrities they follow,\nmerges results by score (timestamp + ranking), returns unified feed. Merge adds ~10-20ms to read path.","height":35,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#374151","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1954756732,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":637,"width":820.02099609375},{"seed":315884740,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"9nK8pUvoFrB7Y8mBAkD6b","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"New tradeoff: Read path now has conditional complexity — must maintain celebrity_list per user, merge two result sets.\nThe 1M follower threshold must be dynamically adjustable. A borderline celebrity (900K followers) is tricky.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b33","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"New tradeoff: Read path now has conditional complexity — must maintain celebrity_list per user, merge two result sets.\nThe 1M follower threshold must be dynamically adjustable. A borderline celebrity (900K followers) is tricky.","height":35,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b45309","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1925684548,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":677,"width":817.9349365234375},{"seed":1996409924,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"NSuXcedlXYKn3ZEUhdbbG","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":16,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"te