re: unix_timestamp\n  TTL: 7 days\n  ZADD \/ ZRANGE by score\n\nKey query:\n  ZADD feed:alice 1709123456 post:xyz\n  ZREVRANGE feed:alice 0 19 WITHSCORES","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b3l","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"posts table:\n  post_id    UUID  PK\n  author_id  UUID  FK+IDX\n  content    TEXT\n  media_url  TEXT\n  status     ENUM(pending,live)\n  created_at TIMESTAMPTZ\n  IDX: (author_id, created_at DESC)\n\nRedis feed cache:\n  Key: feed:{user_id}\n  Type: Sorted Set\n  Member: post_id\n  Score: unix_timestamp\n  TTL: 7 days\n  ZADD \/ ZRANGE by score\n\nKey query:\n  ZADD feed:alice 1709123456 post:xyz\n  ZREVRANGE feed:alice 0 19 WITHSCORES","height":325,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1489687108,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":948.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":1257,"width":284.54373168945312},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#8b5cf6","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b3m","backgroundColor":"#d0bfff","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"ksXAW7KYZFjUtXTywMqpC","x":-251.5596923828125,"seed":912586308,"boundElements":[{"type":"text","id":"9pFVDWuFeaajLfa6VTS_j"}],"y":1529,"opacity":100,"height":44,"width":1530,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":196436988},{"seed":779455940,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"9pFVDWuFeaajLfa6VTS_j","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":19,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"middle","updated":1772747707449,"locked":false,"text":"DEEP DIVE 2 — FR3: Feed Retrieval (Hybrid Merge at Read Time)","version":7,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b3n","roundness":null,"containerId":"ksXAW7KYZFjUtXTywMqpC","originalText":"DEEP DIVE 2 — FR3: Feed Retrieval (Hybrid Merge at Read Time)","height":23.75,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#8b5cf6","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":936439548,"textAlign":"center","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":200.71929931640625,"angle":0,"y":1539.125,"width":625.4420166015625},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#adb5bd","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b3o","backgroundColor":"#f8f9fa","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"HbrCf9n-vfzfJwjNvTD43","x":-251.5596923828125,"seed":394736964,"boundElements":[],"y":1584,"opacity":100,"height":270,"width":490,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":199197820},{"seed":1324870852,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"gV0XoqX_V4BF258WZ5UKA","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":17,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"A. User Journey + Latency Budget","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b3p","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"A. User Journey + Latency Budget","height":21.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#5b21b6","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1193677124,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":1592,"width":285.12371826171875},{"seed":1449505860,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"2zLg9mZ69OAc86NlseVHr","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"1. User opens app or pulls to refresh\n2. Client calls GET \/feed?cursor=null&limit=20\n3. Server checks Redis cache — hit or miss?\n   HIT:  return in <30ms\n   MISS: compute from DB, populate, return in <200ms\n4. Client renders 20 posts\n5. User scrolls — GET \/feed?cursor=<last_score>\n\nDuring failure:\n- Redis down: fallback to DB query path.\n  Latency spikes to 200-500ms. Add circuit\n  breaker: serve stale cached feed if DB also slow.\n- Celebrity DB query slow: serve precomputed\n  feed without celebrity posts (degrade gracefully).\n\nLatency budget breakdown (P99 < 500ms):\n  Redis ZRANGE lookup:          5ms\n  Celebrity posts DB query:    20ms\n  Merge + rank 20+20 posts:     5ms\n  Post metadata hydration:     15ms\n  Network + serialization:     20ms\n  Total:                    ~65ms P50\n                           ~500ms P99 (cache miss)","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b3q","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"1. User opens app or pulls to refresh\n2. Client calls GET \/feed?cursor=null&limit=20\n3. Server checks Redis cache — hit or miss?\n   HIT:  return in <30ms\n   MISS: compute from DB, populate, return in <200ms\n4. Client renders 20 posts\n5. User scrolls — GET \/feed?cursor=<last_score>\n\nDuring failure:\n- Redis down: fallback to DB query path.\n  Latency spikes to 200-500ms. Add circuit\n  breaker: serve stale cached feed if DB also slow.\n- Celebrity DB query slow: serve precomputed\n  feed without celebrity posts (degrade gracefully).\n\nLatency budget breakdown (P99 < 500ms):\n  Redis ZRANGE lookup:          5ms\n  Celebrity posts DB query:    20ms\n  Merge + rank 20+20 posts:     5ms\n  Post metadata hydration:     15ms\n  Network + serialization:     20ms\n  Total:                    ~65ms P50\n                           ~500ms P99 (cache miss)","height":402.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":854693116,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":1617,"width":372.7215576171875},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#adb5bd","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b3r","backgroundColor":"#f8f9fa","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"GqJUqpKrnJV4eGok4wqi1","x":258.4403076171875,"seed":1269730244,"boundElements":[],"y":1584,"opacity":100,"height":270,"width":670,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1583040708},{"seed":1626370884,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"Efe79Ipk6lMifCSaps_tr","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":17,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"B. Internal Flow (Hybrid Read Path)","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b3s","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"B. Internal Flow (Hybrid Read Path)","height":21.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#5b21b6","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1047369084,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":268.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":1592,"width":300.9677734375},{"seed":1418291908,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"gVk5vw994bJ223692FXXe","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":13,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"1. GET \/feed  — auth check via JWT (API gateway)\n2. Check Redis: ZREVRANGEBYSCORE feed:{uid}\n   HIT  -> go to step 6\n   MISS -> go to step 3\n3. [MISS] Fetch followee list from Cassandra\n4. [MISS] SELECT posts WHERE author_id IN (...)\n   ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 20 per shard\n5. [MISS] ZADD feed:{uid} (populate cache, TTL 7d)\n6. Fetch celebrity list: GET celebrity_follows:{uid}\n7. If not empty: SELECT * FROM celebrity_posts\n   WHERE author_id IN (celeb_ids)\n   AND created_at > cursor_timestamp LIMIT 20\n8. Merge: interleave precomputed + celebrity posts\n   sorted by ranking_score (recency + engagement)\n9. Apply mute\/block filter list (Redis SET lookup)\n10. Paginate: return top 20, cursor = lowest score\n11. Hydrate: JOIN users table for author metadata\n    (cached in Redis user_profile:{uid}, TTL 1h)\n12. Return JSON response\n\nCritical path: steps 2,6,7,8,10 (all fast if cached)\nSlow path: steps 3,4,5 (cache miss — DB round trips)","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b3t","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"1. GET \/feed  — auth check via JWT (API gateway)\n2. Check Redis: ZREVRANGEBYSCORE feed:{uid}\n   HIT  -> go to step 6\n   MISS -> go to step 3\n3. [MISS] Fetch followee list from Cassandra\n4. [MISS] SELECT posts WHERE author_id IN (...)\n   ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 20 per shard\n5. [MISS] ZADD feed:{uid} (populate cache, TTL 7d)\n6. Fetch celebrity list: GET celebrity_follows:{uid}\n7. If not empty: SELECT * FROM celebrity_posts\n   WHERE author_id IN (celeb_ids)\n   AND created_at > cursor_timestamp LIMIT 20\n8. Merge: interleave precomputed + celebrity posts\n   sorted by ranking_score (recency + engagement)\n9. Apply mute\/block filter list (Redis SET lookup)\n10. Paginate: return top 20, cursor = lowest score\n11. Hydrate: JOIN users table for author metadata\n    (cached in Redis user_profile:{uid}, TTL 1h)\n12. Return JSON response\n\nCritical path: steps 2,6,7,8,10 (all fast if cached)\nSlow path: steps 3,4,5 (cache miss — DB round trips)","height":357.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1493012548,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":268.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":1617,"width":344.36962890625},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#adb5bd","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b3u","backgroundColor":"#f8f9fa","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"KV2QUVomczfcl87-kvjkD","x":938.4403076171875,"seed":1763144260,"boundElements":[],"y":1584,"opacity":100,"height":270,"width":340,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1804961276},{"seed":1568180676,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"LyB3bgmSelu9uXw7pXvgK","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":17,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"C. Data Model","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b3v","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"C. Data Model","height":21.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#5b21b6","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1726670788,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":948.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":1592,"width":117.65689086914062},{"seed":1691005252,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"pEYoXsatBzAec-ezMjNFh","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":13,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Redis feed cache:\n  Key:    feed:{user_id}\n  Type:   Sorted Set\n  Score:  ranking_score (float)\n  Member: post_id\n  ZREVRANGEBYSCORE feed:alice\n    +inf (cursor_score) LIMIT 0 20\n\nCursor design:\n  cursor = base64(score:post_id)\n  Stable even when new posts arrive\n  No offset shifting on live feed\n\nCelebrity follows:\n  Key: celebrity_follows:{user_id}\n  Type: Redis Set\n  Member: author_id\n  Populated on follow if author\n  follower_count > 1M threshold\n\nPost hydration cache:\n  Key: post:{post_id}\n  Type: Redis Hash\n  Fields: author, content, media_url,\n          like_count, comment_count\n  TTL: 1 hour\n\nMost common query (cache miss):\n  SELECT p.* FROM posts p\n  WHERE p.author_id = ANY(:followees)\n  AND p.created_at > :since\n  ORDER BY created_at DESC\n  LIMIT 20","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b3w","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Redis feed cache:\n  Key:    feed:{user_id}\n  Type:   Sorted Set\n  Score:  ranking_score (float)\n  Member: post_id\n  ZREVRANGEBYSCORE feed:alice\n    +inf (cursor_score) LIMIT 0 20\n\nCursor design:\n  cursor = base64(score:post_id)\n  Stable even when new posts arrive\n  No offset shifting on live feed\n\nCelebrity follows:\n  Key: celebrity_follows:{user_id}\n  Type: Redis Set\n  Member: author_id\n  Populated on follow if author\n  follower_count > 1M threshold\n\nPost hydration cache:\n  Key: post:{post_id}\n  Type: Redis Hash\n  Fields: author, content, media_url,\n          like_count, comment_count\n  TTL: 1 hour\n\nMost common query (cache miss):\n  SELECT p.* FROM posts p\n  WHERE p.author_id = ANY(:followees)\n  AND p.created_at > :since\n  ORDER BY created_at DESC\n  LIMIT 20","height":536.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":2137745020,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":948.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":1617,"width":248.05268859863281},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#06b6d4","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b3x","backgroundColor":"#c3fae8","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"QNhYZZ0QKcJTMVED4UQXi","x":-251.5596923828125,"seed":510388420,"boundElements":[{"type":"text","id":"97PAGFFcxoilgByMIX_ef"}],"y":1949,"opacity":100,"height":44,"width":1530,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":205606724},{"seed":234500164,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"97PAGFFcxoilgByMIX_ef","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":19,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"middle","updated":1772747707449,"locked":false,"text":"DEEP DIVE 3 — FR5: Like \/ React (Counter Aggregation at Scale)","version":7,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b3y","roundness":null,"containerId":"QNhYZZ0QKcJTMVED4UQXi","originalText":"DEEP DIVE 3 — FR5: Like \/ React (Counter Aggregation at Scale)","height":23.75,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#06b6d4","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1649520508,"textAlign":"center","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":199.73129272460938,"angle":0,"y":1959.125,"width":627.41802978515625},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#adb5bd","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b3z","backgroundColor":"#f8f9fa","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"IZEnxlnB9k1DTzuu7uZZm","x":-251.5596923828125,"seed":324241348,"boundElements":[],"y":2004,"opacity":100,"height":265,"width":490,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":425641668},{"seed":1653993284,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"tbsuAY-IVJnWfzR8JMmQm","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":17,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"A. User Journey","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b40","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"A. User Journey","height":21.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#0e7490","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1172895612,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":2012,"width":130.79788208007812},{"seed":2082432708,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"acZkPG3QouE2XEZtzBX4n","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"1. User double-taps a post (Instagram) or\n   clicks the heart button\n2. Client OPTIMISTICALLY updates UI immediately\n   (shows heart filled, increments count by 1)\n3. Client sends POST \/likes  {post_id, user_id}\n4. Server responds 200 in <50ms\n5. Like count on post updates for all viewers\n   within ~30 seconds (eventual consistency)\n\nDuring failure:\n- Server returns 5xx: client rolls back optimistic\n  update, shows error toast. User retries.\n- Redis INCR fails: fallback to queuing like event\n  in Kafka for async retry. Count eventually correct.\n- Like flusher fails: Redis has correct count,\n  DB stale but Redis is source of truth until flush.\n\nLatency budget (P99 < 200ms):\n  Auth check (JWT):           2ms\n  Idempotency check (Redis):  3ms\n  Redis SADD liked_by set:    3ms\n  Redis INCR like_count key:  2ms\n  Publish to Kafka:           5ms\n  Return 200:                 5ms\n  Total:                  ~20ms P50 \/ ~150ms P99","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b41","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"1. User double-taps a post (Instagram) or\n   clicks the heart button\n2. Client OPTIMISTICALLY updates UI immediately\n   (shows heart filled, increments count by 1)\n3. Client sends POST \/likes  {post_id, user_id}\n4. Server responds 200 in <50ms\n5. Like count on post updates for all viewers\n   within ~30 seconds (eventual consistency)\n\nDuring failure:\n- Server returns 5xx: client rolls back optimistic\n  update, shows error toast. User retries.\n- Redis INCR fails: fallback to queuing like event\n  in Kafka for async retry. Count eventually correct.\n- Like flusher fails: Redis has correct count,\n  DB stale but Redis is source of truth until flush.\n\nLatency budget (P99 < 200ms):\n  Auth check (JWT):           2ms\n  Idempotency check (Redis):  3ms\n  Redis SADD liked_by set:    3ms\n  Redis INCR like_count key:  2ms\n  Publish to Kafka:           5ms\n  Return 200:                 5ms\n  Total:                  ~20ms P50 \/ ~150ms P99","height":437.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":585190980,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":2037,"width":355.80963134765625},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#adb5bd","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b42","backgroundColor":"#f8f9fa","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"aBnxL2vY-4mB0l_TTZzvu","x":258.4403076171875,"seed":613281348,"boundElements":[],"y":2004,"opacity":100,"height":265,"width":670,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1901373436},{"seed":1556055492,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"rxj2DGZ-nyu4NQToX8Qye","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":17,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"B. Internal Flow","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b43","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"B. Internal Flow","height":21.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#0e7490","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":2040980932,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":268.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":2012,"width":134.53788757324219},{"seed":1506946372,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"dgS4w4ba0KmC_PUsfUkqp","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":13,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"LIKE PATH:\n1. POST \/likes {post_id, user_id, reaction_type}\n2. JWT auth verify (API gateway)\n3. Idempotency: SISMEMBER liked_by:{post_id} {uid}\n   Already liked? Return 200 (no-op, idempotent)\n4. SADD liked_by:{post_id} {user_id}  [dedup set]\n5. INCR like_count:{post_id}           [fast counter]\n6. Publish like_event to Kafka         [async notify]\n7. Return {post_id, new_count} 200\n\nUNLIKE PATH:\n3b. SREM liked_by:{post_id} {user_id}\n5b. DECR like_count:{post_id}\n\nASYNC FLUSH (every 30 seconds):\n- Like Flusher service reads like_count:{post_id}\n  from Redis for all dirty post_ids\n- Single UPDATE posts SET like_count = :n\n  WHERE post_id = :id  (one query per post)\n- Marks post_id as flushed in flush_state set\n\nCRITICAL PATH (on the latency path):\n  Steps 2,3,4,5 — all Redis ops, <10ms total\n  Step 6 async — NOT on critical path\n  DB write — NOT on critical path (async flush)\n\nHOT POST HANDLING:\n  Viral post: liked_by set could grow to millions.\n  Cap liked_by set at 10M members.\n  Use HyperLogLog for approximate counts >10M.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b44","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"LIKE PATH:\n1. POST \/likes {post_id, user_id, reaction_type}\n2. JWT auth verify (API gateway)\n3. Idempotency: SISMEMBER liked_by:{post_id} {uid}\n   Already liked? Return 200 (no-op, idempotent)\n4. SADD liked_by:{post_id} {user_id}  [dedup set]\n5. INCR like_count:{post_id}           [fast counter]\n6. Publish like_event to Kafka         [async notify]\n7. Return {post_id, new_count} 200\n\nUNLIKE PATH:\n3b. SREM liked_by:{post_id} {user_id}\n5b. DECR like_count:{post_id}\n\nASYNC FLUSH (every 30 seconds):\n- Like Flusher service reads like_count:{post_id}\n  from Redis for all dirty post_ids\n- Single UPDATE posts SET like_count = :n\n  WHERE post_id = :id  (one query per post)\n- Marks post_id as flushed in flush_state set\n\nCRITICAL PATH (on the latency path):\n  Steps 2,3,4,5 — all Redis ops, <10ms total\n  Step 6 async — NOT on critical path\n  DB write — NOT on critical path (async flush)\n\nHOT POST HANDLING:\n  Viral post: liked_by set could grow to millions.\n  Cap liked_by set at 10M members.\n  Use HyperLogLog for approximate counts >10M.","height":487.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":83249276,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":268.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":2037,"width":344.79864501953125},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#adb5bd","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b45","backgroundColor":"#f8f9fa","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"lFP-6M3DG4vnY3ns6sRim","x":938.4403076171875,"seed":2099504324,"boundElements":[],"y":2004,"opacity":100,"height":265,"width":340,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":583896388},{"seed":1280486468,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"w8JXvlonF4N9dMVstNrKZ","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":17,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"C. Data Model","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b46","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"C. Data Model","height":21.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#0e7490","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1687148796,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":948.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":2012,"width":117.65689086914062},{"seed":1765573572,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"DdX16pjllekhxZUUPNI6e","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":13,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Redis (source of truth for counts):\n  like_count:{post_id}\n    Type: String (integer)\n    INCR \/ DECR\n    No TTL (permanent)\n\n  liked_by:{post_id}\n    Type: Set\n    SADD \/ SREM \/ SISMEMBER\n    Cap: 10M members\n    TTL: 90 days\n\n  liked_posts:{user_id}\n    Type: Set\n    For 'did I like this?' check\n    TTL: 30 days\n\nDB (durable, slightly stale):\n  likes table:\n    post_id   UUID  IDX\n    user_id   UUID  IDX\n    created_at TIMESTAMPTZ\n    UNIQUE (post_id, user_id)\n\n  posts.like_count INT\n    Updated by async flusher\n\nSchema decision:\n  liked_by as Redis SET not DB table\n  because 'did I like?' is a hot-path\n  read needing <5ms, not a join.\n  DB likes table is for analytics\n  and recovery only, not hot path.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b47","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Redis (source of truth for counts):\n  like_count:{post_id}\n    Type: String (integer)\n    INCR \/ DECR\n    No TTL (permanent)\n\n  liked_by:{post_id}\n    Type: Set\n    SADD \/ SREM \/ SISMEMBER\n    Cap: 10M members\n    TTL: 90 days\n\n  liked_posts:{user_id}\n    Type: Set\n    For 'did I like this?' check\n    TTL: 30 days\n\nDB (durable, slightly stale):\n  likes table:\n    post_id   UUID  IDX\n    user_id   UUID  IDX\n    created_at TIMESTAMPTZ\n    UNIQUE (post_id, user_id)\n\n  posts.like_count INT\n    Updated by async flusher\n\nSchema decision:\n  liked_by as Redis SET not DB table\n  because 'did I like?' is a hot-path\n  read needing <5ms, not a join.\n  DB likes table is for analytics\n  and recovery only, not hot path.","height":536.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1337148612,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":948.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":2037,"width":243.55476379394531},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#4a9eed","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b48","backgroundColor":"#1e1e2e","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"uOXn4T6FYQFnATL7vPez3","x":-251.5596923828125,"seed":167734084,"boundElements":[],"y":2284,"opacity":100,"height":95,"width":1530,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":732125564},{"seed":1895391940,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"PJjB4FynyPh5EwyO3Z_dN","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":17,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Deep Dive Key Patterns:","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b49","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Deep Dive Key Patterns:","height":21.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#a5d8ff","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1442188356,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":2294,"width":202.96284484863281},{"seed":1690856004,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"VuWWhkKNVo4Ya9VrgKO1_","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":15,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Fan-out: Kafka decouples write from propagation. Idempotency key in Redis prevents duplicate posts.  |  Feed Read: cursor=(score:post_id) gives stable pagination on live feed.\nHybrid merge: Redis sorted set + celebrity DB query merged at read time under 500ms P99.  |  Likes: Redis INCR as hot counter, async flush to DB every 30s. SADD set for dedup = idempotent unlike.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4A","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Fan-out: Kafka decouples write from propagation. Idempotency key in Redis prevents duplicate posts.  |  Feed Read: cursor=(score:post_id) gives stable pagination on live feed.\nHybrid merge: Redis sorted set + celebrity DB query merged at read time under 500ms P99.  |  Likes: Redis INCR as hot counter, async flush to DB every 30s. SADD set for dedup = idempotent unlike.","height":37.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#e5e5e5","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":896715260,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":2320,"width":1476.1041259765625},{"seed":675971524,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"KCesis2Otvy1kq4LBZn0a","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":26,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"NEWS FEED — Step 9: Failure Handling","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4B","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"NEWS FEED — Step 9: Failure Handling","height":32.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":661906372,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":108.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":2487,"width":495.09170532226562},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#ef4444","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b4C","backgroundColor":"#ffc9c9","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"caS4qa2I1k5RejbfryZmD","x":-251.5596923828125,"seed":1922935108,"boundElements":[],"y":2527,"opacity":100,"height":195,"width":740,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":620767868},{"seed":1730142404,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"ybk51bsaFhRC29Snn-gxI","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":18,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Client Errors (4xx) — Validate Early, Fail Fast","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4D","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Client Errors (4xx) — Validate Early, Fail Fast","height":22.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b91c1c","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1246415684,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":2535,"width":407.6817626953125},{"seed":225388612,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"IU91sp6rj7k9dGwpmuWEW","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Validate WHERE: API gateway before any downstream call.\nNever let invalid data reach Kafka or the DB.\n\n400 Bad Request:  missing post content, invalid media type\n401 Unauthorized: missing\/expired JWT — no retry\n403 Forbidden:    posting to private group you're not in\n409 Conflict:     duplicate idempotency_key (return cached response)\n413 Too Large:    post content >10KB, video >500MB\n\nReturn: structured JSON error body with error_code + human message.\nClient behavior: show user error, NO automatic retry.\nNO message queued, NO worker triggered, NO DB touched.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4E","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Validate WHERE: API gateway before any downstream call.\nNever let invalid data reach Kafka or the DB.\n\n400 Bad Request:  missing post content, invalid media type\n401 Unauthorized: missing\/expired JWT — no retry\n403 Forbidden:    posting to private group you're not in\n409 Conflict:     duplicate idempotency_key (return cached response)\n413 Too Large:    post content >10KB, video >500MB\n\nReturn: structured JSON error body with error_code + human message.\nClient behavior: show user error, NO automatic retry.\nNO message queued, NO worker triggered, NO DB touched.","height":210,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1829599996,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":2561,"width":484.511474609375},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#f59e0b","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b4F","backgroundColor":"#ffd8a8","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"pAp1a9Da-Ajjf1O2yKCV9","x":508.4403076171875,"seed":1231650756,"boundElements":[],"y":2527,"opacity":100,"height":195,"width":770,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1356382916},{"seed":1395451716,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"5RS5jzFQUTlsWIsSgs7Di","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":18,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"External \/ Provider Failures","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4G","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"External \/ Provider Failures","height":22.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b45309","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1478278012,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":518.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":2535,"width":244.74581909179688},{"seed":790060740,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"RPPWad87ibWept0lJ0GPQ","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"S3 upload fails:\n  Circuit breaker opens after 5 failures in 10s.\n  Fallback: return presigned URL to client anyway.\n  Client retries upload directly — server not in loop.\n\nCDN origin unreachable:\n  Serve stale cached media from CDN edge (TTL extended).\n  Alert if origin down >60s.\n\nKafka broker unavailable:\n  Producer: retry with backoff (max 3 attempts, 500ms\/1s\/2s).\n  Fallback: write fan-out task to outbox table in DB.\n  Outbox poller picks up and publishes when Kafka recovers.\n  Guarantees at-least-once fan-out even during broker outage.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4H","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"S3 upload fails:\n  Circuit breaker opens after 5 failures in 10s.\n  Fallback: return presigned URL to client anyway.\n  Client retries upload directly — server not in loop.\n\nCDN origin unreachable:\n  Serve stale cached media from CDN edge (TTL extended).\n  Alert if origin down >60s.\n\nKafka broker unavailable:\n  Producer: retry with backoff (max 3 attempts, 500ms\/1s\/2s).\n  Fallback: write fan-out task to outbox table in DB.\n  Outbox poller picks up and publishes when Kafka recovers.\n  Guarantees at-least-once fan-out even during broker outage.","height":245,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1371261508,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":518.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":2561,"width":436.04348754882812},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#8b5cf6","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b4I","backgroundColor":"#d0bfff","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"3EFZF7rx3WiVdX_3KZ0Bk","x":-251.5596923828125,"seed":633792068,"boundElements":[],"y":2737,"opacity":100,"height":220,"width":740,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":275770364},{"seed":1008303556,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"yz5b6F6AgR_6HVGWSF1uw","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":18,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Internal Service Failures — Saga + Compensation","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4J","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Internal Service Failures — Saga + Compensation","height":22.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#5b21b6","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1607590340,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":2745,"width":426.68972778320312},{"seed":724378948,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"5hUI2NaGQYshf6SL3CQZQ","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Fan-out worker crash mid-fan-out:\n  Kafka offset NOT committed until batch complete.\n  Worker restarts, reprocesses from last offset.\n  ZADD to Redis is IDEMPOTENT — same (post_id, score)\n  added twice = no-op. Safe to replay.\n\nPost created but Kafka publish fails (rare):\n  Transactional outbox pattern:\n  1. INSERT post + INSERT outbox_event in same DB txn.\n  2. Outbox poller reads unflushed events, publishes to Kafka.\n  3. Marks event as published. Guarantees exactly-once semantics.\n\nFeed hydration service down:\n  Return cached feed from Redis without metadata hydration.\n  Degrade gracefully: show post_ids + author names from cache,\n  skip real-time like counts. Better stale than empty.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4K","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Fan-out worker crash mid-fan-out:\n  Kafka offset NOT committed until batch complete.\n  Worker restarts, reprocesses from last offset.\n  ZADD to Redis is IDEMPOTENT — same (post_id, score)\n  added twice = no-op. Safe to replay.\n\nPost created but Kafka publish fails (rare):\n  Transactional outbox pattern:\n  1. INSERT post + INSERT outbox_event in same DB txn.\n  2. Outbox poller reads unflushed events, publishes to Kafka.\n  3. Marks event as published. Guarantees exactly-once semantics.\n\nFeed hydration service down:\n  Return cached feed from Redis without metadata hydration.\n  Degrade gracefully: show post_ids + author names from cache,\n  skip real-time like counts. Better stale than empty.","height":280,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":671681660,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":2771,"width":452.60552978515625},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#06b6d4","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b4L","backgroundColor":"#c3fae8","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"S-z9LWAGzgKZGxMF0Alim","x":508.4403076171875,"seed":1482677444,"boundElements":[],"y":2737,"opacity":100,"height":220,"width":770,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":37292356},{"seed":1297065028,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"bWV0pLUeAmemjJJdXkWjD","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":18,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Infrastructure Failures","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4M","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Infrastructure Failures","height":22.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#0e7490","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":548019452,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":518.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":2745,"width":201.27584838867188},{"seed":802847684,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"US9mOurFpwvIHNSQIBbLg","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Kafka partition down:\n  Kafka rebalances — consumers pick up orphaned partitions.\n  Fan-out lag spike: monitor consumer_lag metric.\n  Alert at lag > 10K messages. No data loss (Kafka replicated).\n\nDB primary fails:\n  Automated failover: replica promoted in ~30s (AWS RDS\/Aurora).\n  During failover: writes queue at connection pool, timeout at 35s.\n  Feed reads: redirect to remaining replicas (reads unaffected).\n  RPO: < 1s (sync replication). RTO: ~30s.\n\nRedis cache node eviction \/ failure:\n  Cache miss spike: DB absorbs traffic (autoscaling triggers).\n  Feed reads degrade to 200-500ms (DB path) not failure.\n  Redis Cluster: surviving nodes serve their key ranges.\n  Populate cache on miss — self-healing within minutes.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4N","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Kafka partition down:\n  Kafka rebalances — consumers pick up orphaned partitions.\n  Fan-out lag spike: monitor consumer_lag metric.\n  Alert at lag > 10K messages. No data loss (Kafka replicated).\n\nDB primary fails:\n  Automated failover: replica promoted in ~30s (AWS RDS\/Aurora).\n  During failover: writes queue at connection pool, timeout at 35s.\n  Feed reads: redirect to remaining replicas (reads unaffected).\n  RPO: < 1s (sync replication). RTO: ~30s.\n\nRedis cache node eviction \/ failure:\n  Cache miss spike: DB absorbs traffic (autoscaling triggers).\n  Feed reads degrade to 200-500ms (DB path) not failure.\n  Redis Cluster: surviving nodes serve their key ranges.\n  Populate cache on miss — self-healing within minutes.","height":280,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":743391428,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":518.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":2771,"width":455.71343994140625},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#f59e0b","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b4O","backgroundColor":"#fff3bf","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"gEjWXn2b3NTmLf6o3AsLj","x":-251.5596923828125,"seed":975070020,"boundElements":[],"y":2971,"opacity":100,"height":200,"width":740,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1943346556},{"seed":846813892,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"D1OBhLfROQkF674RxwJAK","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":18,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Retry Strategy — Exact Specification","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4P","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Retry Strategy — Exact Specification","height":22.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b45309","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":900892740,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":2979,"width":336.59979248046875},{"seed":1669947972,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"MGVyYyk2t23Rh1pLOUezw","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Formula: delay = min(base_ms * 2^attempt + rand(0, jitter_ms), max_ms)\n  base_ms=100, jitter_ms=100, max_ms=30000\n  Attempt 1: ~100-200ms\n  Attempt 2: ~200-400ms\n  Attempt 3: ~400-800ms  -> DLQ after 3 failures\n\nRETRYABLE errors:\n  503 Service Unavailable, 429 Rate Limited,\n  500 Internal (idempotent ops only), network timeout,\n  Kafka produce timeout, Redis connection reset\n\nNON-RETRYABLE errors:\n  400 Bad Request, 401 Unauthorized, 403 Forbidden,\n  409 Conflict (duplicate), 404 Not Found","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4Q","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Formula: delay = min(base_ms * 2^attempt + rand(0, jitter_ms), max_ms)\n  base_ms=100, jitter_ms=100, max_ms=30000\n  Attempt 1: ~100-200ms\n  Attempt 2: ~200-400ms\n  Attempt 3: ~400-800ms  -> DLQ after 3 failures\n\nRETRYABLE errors:\n  503 Service Unavailable, 429 Rate Limited,\n  500 Internal (idempotent ops only), network timeout,\n  Kafka produce timeout, Redis connection reset\n\nNON-RETRYABLE errors:\n  400 Bad Request, 401 Unauthorized, 403 Forbidden,\n  409 Conflict (duplicate), 404 Not Found","height":245,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":449580540,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":3005,"width":495.33343505859375},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#22c55e","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b4R","backgroundColor":"#b2f2bb","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"ODBuScriFcvETxfiK-Y1X","x":508.4403076171875,"seed":338459076,"boundElements":[],"y":2971,"opacity":100,"height":200,"width":770,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1379983300},{"seed":2139136324,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"_vPzBKG2v1oHI9YEPED27","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":18,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Idempotency Implementation — Exact Mechanism","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4S","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Idempotency Implementation — Exact Mechanism","height":22.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#15803d","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":378596988,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":518.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":2979,"width":428.29171752929688},{"seed":1290000580,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"gpEwxPvCEiiqQZgDyde8G","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Post creation dedup key:\n  Hash fields: SHA256(user_id + content_hash + client_ts_minute)\n  Truncate to 64-bit hex. Store as Redis key:\n  SET idem:{hash} {post_id} EX 86400  (24h TTL)\n  On retry: GET idem:{hash} -> return original post_id.\n\nLike idempotency:\n  SADD liked_by:{post_id} {user_id}\n  Returns 0 if already member -> skip INCR, return 200.\n  SADD is atomic — no race condition between check + add.\n\nFan-out worker dedup:\n  ZADD feed:{follower_id} NX score post_id\n  NX flag = 'only add if not exists'.\n  Replay-safe: same post_id never added twice to feed.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4T","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Post creation dedup key:\n  Hash fields: SHA256(user_id + content_hash + client_ts_minute)\n  Truncate to 64-bit hex. Store as Redis key:\n  SET idem:{hash} {post_id} EX 86400  (24h TTL)\n  On retry: GET idem:{hash} -> return original post_id.\n\nLike idempotency:\n  SADD liked_by:{post_id} {user_id}\n  Returns 0 if already member -> skip INCR, return 200.\n  SADD is atomic — no race condition between check + add.\n\nFan-out worker dedup:\n  ZADD feed:{follower_id} NX score post_id\n  NX flag = 'only add if not exists'.\n  Replay-safe: same post_id never added twice to feed.","height":262.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":169363268,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":518.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":3005,"width":455.32147216796875},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#ef4444","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b4U","backgroundColor":"#ffc9c9","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"99tLJe87NIaAbWnR9L6dl","x":-251.5596923828125,"seed":133439556,"boundElements":[],"y":3185,"opacity":100,"height":130,"width":1530,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":2011545340},{"seed":412055492,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"RJYuRN26PcQk7JjwAOzBU","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":18,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Dead Letter Queue (DLQ) — What Triggers It, What Ops Does With It","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4V","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Dead Letter Queue (DLQ) — What Triggers It, What Ops Does With It","height":22.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b91c1c","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":831962820,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":3193,"width":632.681640625},{"seed":986963780,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"JAH1ZC7HJwexZS2Ezev_3","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Triggers DLQ after: 3 retries with exponential backoff ALL fail. Specific causes: malformed message schema, permanently unavailable\ndependency (follower DB shard missing), post_id references deleted post, bug in worker deserialization code.\n\nDLQ = Kafka topic 'fan_out_dlq' with 7-day retention. Ops process:\n1. Alert fires: dlq_message_count > 0 for 5min  2. Engineer inspects message payload + stack trace in logs\n3. Fix root cause (deploy patch, restore DB, fix schema)  4. Replay DLQ messages with kafka-consumer-groups --reset-offsets\n5. Monitor fan-out lag returns to 0  |  SLA: DLQ messages replayed within 4 hours of alert.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4W","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Triggers DLQ after: 3 retries with exponential backoff ALL fail. Specific causes: malformed message schema, permanently unavailable\ndependency (follower DB shard missing), post_id references deleted post, bug in worker deserialization code.\n\nDLQ = Kafka topic 'fan_out_dlq' with 7-day retention. Ops process:\n1. Alert fires: dlq_message_count > 0 for 5min  2. Engineer inspects message payload + stack trace in logs\n3. Fix root cause (deploy patch, restore DB, fix schema)  4. Replay DLQ messages with kafka-consumer-groups --reset-offsets\n5. Monitor fan-out lag returns to 0  |  SLA: DLQ messages replayed within 4 hours of alert.","height":122.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1733066620,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":3219,"width":899.876953125},{"seed":1998542532,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"HtjVi2xDJJ2oUUQQnDR-g","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":26,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"NEWS FEED — Step 10: NFR Coverage Analysis","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4X","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"NEWS FEED — Step 10: NFR Coverage Analysis","height":32.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1633306180,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":88.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":3417,"width":602.263671875},{"seed":437247556,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"sQRydjyWV9W0NqeBEf3zv","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":16,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"For each NFR: which components cover it, what breaks it, honest remaining gaps.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4Y","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"For each NFR: which components cover it, what breaks it, honest remaining gaps.","height":20,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#757575","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":755445756,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":88.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":3451,"width":629.90338134765625},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#ef4444","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b4Z","backgroundColor":"#ffc9c9","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"RypJVaIl7WU-m13mmiBwP","x":-251.5596923828125,"seed":746812868,"boundElements":[],"y":3477,"opacity":100,"height":195,"width":740,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1849744836},{"seed":1805131076,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"WYZT3yyBHU1N1jyHIh0AN","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":18,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Availability — Target: 99.99%","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4a","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Availability — Target: 99.99%","height":22.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b91c1c","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":957862012,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":3485,"width":262.079833984375},{"seed":1085002948,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"PUh9L8kwDJzaAWL8dIV82","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Covered by:\n- Multi-AZ API fleet (150 nodes): single node loss = no impact\n- Redis Cluster: automatic failover, surviving nodes serve their ranges\n- Kafka replication factor 3: broker loss auto-rebalances in <30s\n- Aurora Multi-AZ: automated primary failover in ~30s\n- CDN edge: serves cached media even if origin is down","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4b","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Covered by:\n- Multi-AZ API fleet (150 nodes): single node loss = no impact\n- Redis Cluster: automatic failover, surviving nodes serve their ranges\n- Kafka replication factor 3: broker loss auto-rebalances in <30s\n- Aurora Multi-AZ: automated primary failover in ~30s\n- CDN edge: serves cached media even if origin is down","height":105,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1634239812,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":3511,"width":474.96337890625},{"seed":962370628,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"1N6pXZvdnRlK4KWX8F1pF","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Violated by: All three: Kafka rebalance + Redis failover + DB failover\nhappening simultaneously (cascade). Probability: very low but non-zero.\nRemaining gap: Kafka rebalance causes 10-30s fan-out pause — not\nuser-facing but degrades feed freshness for that window.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4c","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Violated by: All three: Kafka rebalance + Redis failover + DB failover\nhappening simultaneously (cascade). Probability: very low but non-zero.\nRemaining gap: Kafka rebalance causes 10-30s fan-out pause — not\nuser-facing but degrades feed freshness for that window.","height":70,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b45309","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":725639420,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":3609,"width":480.47946166992188},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#ef4444","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b4d","backgroundColor":"#ffc9c9","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"2w6WW_qSfh8syYEApJMoQ","x":508.4403076171875,"seed":2139648964,"boundElements":[],"y":3477,"opacity":100,"height":195,"width":770,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1882143940},{"seed":1364024132,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"WuKLkZ_U28kYJiZZbNldp","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":18,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Latency — Feed P50<80ms, P99<500ms","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4e","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Latency — Feed P50<80ms, P99<500ms","height":22.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b91c1c","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1526915452,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":518.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":3485,"width":351.98980712890625},{"seed":2030654148,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"5peLbM9clRaULg63xj61q","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Covered by:\n- Redis sorted set (ZREVRANGEBYSCORE): P50 ~5ms\n- CDN for all media: zero origin latency for cached assets\n- Precomputed ranked feeds: no ML inference at read time\n- Post metadata Redis cache (TTL 1h): no DB hydration per post\n- Stateless API: no session state lookup on hot path","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4f","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Covered by:\n- Redis sorted set (ZREVRANGEBYSCORE): P50 ~5ms\n- CDN for all media: zero origin latency for cached assets\n- Precomputed ranked feeds: no ML inference at read time\n- Post metadata Redis cache (TTL 1h): no DB hydration per post\n- Stateless API: no session state lookup on hot path","height":105,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1949500484,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":518.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":3511,"width":454.77532958984375},{"seed":1163549252,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"UGKkarXKevwHKhgkf7B0t","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Violated by: Cold cache after mass Redis eviction — all users hit DB\nsimultaneously (thundering herd). Celebrity shard slow query adds\n20-50ms to every read for followers of that celebrity.\nRemaining gap: P99 during cache miss storms not fully protected\nwithout request coalescing (dog-pile prevention).","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4g","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Violated by: Cold cache after mass Redis eviction — all users hit DB\nsimultaneously (thundering herd). Celebrity shard slow query adds\n20-50ms to every read for followers of that celebrity.\nRemaining gap: P99 during cache miss storms not fully protected\nwithout request coalescing (dog-pile prevention).","height":87.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b45309","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1604407804,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":518.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":3609,"width":470.0494384765625},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#f59e0b","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b4h","backgroundColor":"#fff3bf","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"jwBX6O9bxY7Wdfi_XNNvK","x":-251.5596923828125,"seed":18772420,"boundElements":[],"y":3687,"opacity":100,"height":180,"width":740,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1666309060},{"seed":1802737988,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"hF6CC9jRDwjoQQIFmmLtO","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":18,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Throughput — 232K read QPS, 464K like QPS peak","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4i","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Throughput — 232K read QPS, 464K like QPS peak","height":22.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b45309","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":404599420,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":3695,"width":453.3837890625},{"seed":800575684,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"0QGkpt13krrLqgdWTilPf","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Covered by:\n- 150 stateless API nodes: ~300K QPS capacity (@2K each)\n- Redis cluster (6 nodes): ~600K ops\/sec — 2.5x headroom\n- Kafka: handles 115 MB\/s fan-out easily (designed for GB\/s)\n- DB sharding (10 shards x 3 nodes): distributes write load\n- Like counter: Redis INCR handles 100K+\/sec per node","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4j","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Covered by:\n- 150 stateless API nodes: ~300K QPS capacity (@2K each)\n- Redis cluster (6 nodes): ~600K ops\/sec — 2.5x headroom\n- Kafka: handles 115 MB\/s fan-out easily (designed for GB\/s)\n- DB sharding (10 shards x 3 nodes): distributes write load\n- Like counter: Redis INCR handles 100K+\/sec per node","height":105,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1202307908,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":3721,"width":423.03753662109375},{"seed":1569265732,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"4fw7pn_wnAguRayQ71Zzq","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Violated by: Single hot DB shard if one author_id generates\ndisproportionate traffic (not evenly distributed by user_id hash).\nRemaining gap: No autoscaling spec for API tier — need HPA\nconfigured on CPU >70% to handle sudden traffic spikes.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4k","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Violated by: Single hot DB shard if one author_id generates\ndisproportionate traffic (not evenly distributed by user_id hash).\nRemaining gap: No autoscaling spec for API tier — need HPA\nconfigured on CPU >70% to handle sudden traffic spikes.","height":70,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b45309","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":859439868,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":3817,"width":448.74136352539062},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#f59e0b","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b4l","backgroundColor":"#fff3bf","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"I0uhvMmxMpHGT9kr7rns5","x":508.4403076171875,"seed":1623551940,"boundElements":[],"y":3687,"opacity":100,"height":180,"width":770,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":932756164},{"seed":2039142212,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"dHu9_YcJO93mDLjNnnLaa","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":18,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Durability — 99.9999% (zero post loss)","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4m","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Durability — 99.9999% (zero post loss)","height":22.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b45309","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":930628476,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":518.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":3695,"width":352.72775268554688},{"seed":876039876,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"HMW-8k-dun3ArTDf1dQOz","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Covered by:\n- Sync DB write before 200 returned to client\n- WAL replication to 2 replicas (Aurora: synchronous)\n- S3 for media: 11-nines durability by design\n- Transactional outbox: post + fan-out event atomically committed\n- Cross-region backup: daily snapshot to secondary region","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4n","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Covered by:\n- Sync DB write before 200 returned to client\n- WAL replication to 2 replicas (Aurora: synchronous)\n- S3 for media: 11-nines durability by design\n- Transactional outbox: post + fan-out event atomically committed\n- Cross-region backup: daily snapshot to secondary region","height":105,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1304216132,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":518.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":3721,"width":457.65951538085938},{"seed":1634260548,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"sCO-XumiftZvs5k1aF4mS","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Violated by: Bug where API returns 200 before DB commit\nconfirmed (async write anti-pattern). Redis-only write without\nDB fallback for like counts during flush failure.\nRemaining gap: Like counts since last flush are in Redis only\n— Redis AOF persistence required to close this gap.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4o","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Violated by: Bug where API returns 200 before DB commit\nconfirmed (async write anti-pattern). Redis-only write without\nDB fallback for like counts during flush failure.\nRemaining gap: Like counts since last flush are in Redis only\n— Redis AOF persistence required to close this gap.","height":87.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b45309","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":186283004,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":518.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":3817,"width":425.89349365234375},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#22c55e","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b4p","backgroundColor":"#b2f2bb","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"KljYMq0fmvGSgx8tUs4rH","x":-251.5596923828125,"seed":234712516,"boundElements":[],"y":3882,"opacity":100,"height":185,"width":740,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":552851908},{"seed":2064848196,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"ugle2ys5xX6X-KscaUUaK","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":18,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Consistency — RYOW for follow\/unfollow, Eventual for feed","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4q","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Consistency — RYOW for follow\/unfollow, Eventual for feed","height":22.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#15803d","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":2082641020,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":3890,"width":526.7877197265625},{"seed":369609924,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"pVzCeyUC76qYrctzAepsw","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Covered by:\n- Social graph reads routed to DB primary only (RYOW guarantee)\n- Feed content from Redis (eventual — up to 5s lag acceptable)\n- Like counts eventual via Redis (30s DB flush lag acceptable)\n- Follow invalidates Redis feed cache immediately (sync)\n- Unfollow: cache cleared + filter applied at read time as safety net","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4r","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Covered by:\n- Social graph reads routed to DB primary only (RYOW guarantee)\n- Feed content from Redis (eventual — up to 5s lag acceptable)\n- Like counts eventual via Redis (30s DB flush lag acceptable)\n- Follow invalidates Redis feed cache immediately (sync)\n- Unfollow: cache cleared + filter applied at read time as safety net","height":105,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1012662596,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":3916,"width":463.693359375},{"seed":1887016004,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"TJYQpraP8REmjW0M4FoTv","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Violated by: User switches between geographic regions mid-session\n— their session may route to a replica in the new region that\nhasn't yet received the unfollow WAL entry (<500ms lag).\nRemaining gap: Cross-region RYOW requires session affinity\nor global primary routing for social graph ops.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4s","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Violated by: User switches between geographic regions mid-session\n— their session may route to a replica in the new region that\nhasn't yet received the unfollow WAL entry (<500ms lag).\nRemaining gap: Cross-region RYOW requires session affinity\nor global primary routing for social graph ops.","height":87.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b45309","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1213375740,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":4017,"width":452.59136962890625},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#22c55e","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b4t","backgroundColor":"#b2f2bb","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"sWl_ZUjvljBpfM7xmFf8m","x":508.4403076171875,"seed":944139204,"boundElements":[],"y":3882,"opacity":100,"height":185,"width":770,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":391329988},{"seed":797725508,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"9tQR8kHpGFofmAZ-75CPg","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":18,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Idempotency — Duplicate detection on all writes","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4u","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Idempotency — Duplicate detection on all writes","height":22.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#15803d","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":623682940,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":518.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":3890,"width":428.20172119140625},{"seed":615074500,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"lFyNDS_XAWt1rXNjcSs_D","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Covered by:\n- Post creation: SHA256 content fingerprint in Redis (TTL 24h)\n- Like: Redis SADD returns 0 if already member — atomic dedup\n- Fan-out: ZADD NX — only adds if post_id not already in feed\n- Follow: UNIQUE constraint on (follower_id, followee_id) in DB\n- Kafka consumer: tracks processed offsets — no double-consume","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4v","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Covered by:\n- Post creation: SHA256 content fingerprint in Redis (TTL 24h)\n- Like: Redis SADD returns 0 if already member — atomic dedup\n- Fan-out: ZADD NX — only adds if post_id not already in feed\n- Follow: UNIQUE constraint on (follower_id, followee_id) in DB\n- Kafka consumer: tracks processed offsets — no double-consume","height":105,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":225935428,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":518.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":3916,"width":447.91552734375},{"seed":1782272580,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"V4AkmJlhOG1tWTjiJ5NXO","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Violated by: Redis idempotency key expiry (after 24h) allows\nthe same content re-posted 25h later to be deduped incorrectly.\nThis is acceptable — 24h window is intentional product decision.\nRemaining gap: Cross-region idempotency key sync if user posts\nfrom two regions simultaneously (race condition).","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4w","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Violated by: Redis idempotency key expiry (after 24h) allows\nthe same content re-posted 25h later to be deduped incorrectly.\nThis is acceptable — 24h window is intentional product decision.\nRemaining gap: Cross-region idempotency key sync if user posts\nfrom two regions simultaneously (race condition).","height":87.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b45309","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1207080444,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":518.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":4017,"width":445.17138671875},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#8b5cf6","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b4x","backgroundColor":"#d0bfff","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"bNcUHkbygoJQEOoWrSdib","x":-251.5596923828125,"seed":1327524292,"boundElements":[],"y":4082,"opacity":100,"height":175,"width":740,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1453774788},{"seed":376869188,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"6X4hCUIoIZ8lj8_9hLxVr","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":18,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Security — Auth, Private Accounts, Rate Limits","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4y","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Security — Auth, Private Accounts, Rate Limits","height":22.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#5b21b6","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1839625852,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":4090,"width":420.1917724609375},{"seed":1872480452,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"uO5xlKfsVPPwq3vIgrtNK","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Covered by:\n- JWT verified at API gateway on every request\n- Private account check: feed service enforces follow-check\n  before returning any content from private profiles\n- Rate limiting: 100 feed reads\/min, 10 posts\/min (token bucket)\n- TLS everywhere: all internal service communication encrypted\n- Input sanitization: content HTML-escaped at write time","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b4z","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Covered by:\n- JWT verified at API gateway on every request\n- Private account check: feed service enforces follow-check\n  before returning any content from private profiles\n- Rate limiting: 100 feed reads\/min, 10 posts\/min (token bucket)\n- TLS everywhere: all internal service communication encrypted\n- Input sanitization: content HTML-escaped at write time","height":122.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":2130657092,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":4116,"width":440.28546142578125},{"seed":1848512580,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"t6n01n_J_QZTuHabr78u8","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Violated by: Celebrity read path query at read time (V6) must\nalso enforce private-account visibility — easy to miss in merge.\nRemaining gap: Mute\/block lists not applied in celebrity_posts\nmerge path — private posts of muted celebrities could appear.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b50","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Violated by: Celebrity read path query at read time (V6) must\nalso enforce private-account visibility — easy to miss in merge.\nRemaining gap: Mute\/block lists not applied in celebrity_posts\nmerge path — private posts of muted celebrities could appear.","height":70,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b45309","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1661617916,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":4211,"width":428.88946533203125},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#8b5cf6","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b51","backgroundColor":"#d0bfff","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"bkZ0_aTkSi_5sBMR-yNlh","x":508.4403076171875,"seed":34301892,"boundElements":[],"y":4082,"opacity":100,"height":175,"width":770,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1591654084},{"seed":1867632452,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"d3QjtY7r8mVsbZOmKTvb6","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":18,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Observability — Metrics, Traces, Alerts","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b52","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Observability — Metrics, Traces, Alerts","height":22.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#5b21b6","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":211814268,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":518.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":4090,"width":344.68170166015625},{"seed":1180649156,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"3BMZ3L50SznNimEu9Rk74","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Covered by:\n- Distributed traces: OTEL on all service calls (Jaeger\/Tempo)\n- Metrics: Prometheus + Grafana dashboards\n  Key: feed_p99_ms, cache_hit_ratio, fan_out_lag_s\n- Kafka consumer lag: per-topic, per-partition monitoring\n- Structured logs: JSON with trace_id, user_id, post_id\n- SLO burn rate alerts: page if error budget burns >5x rate","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b53","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Covered by:\n- Distributed traces: OTEL on all service calls (Jaeger\/Tempo)\n- Metrics: Prometheus + Grafana dashboards\n  Key: feed_p99_ms, cache_hit_ratio, fan_out_lag_s\n- Kafka consumer lag: per-topic, per-partition monitoring\n- Structured logs: JSON with trace_id, user_id, post_id\n- SLO burn rate alerts: page if error budget burns >5x rate","height":122.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":316882500,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":518.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":4116,"width":429.2254638671875},{"seed":1540476484,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"OwZrhhm6pEWwwmZxG5YFy","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Violated by: Fan-out lag tracked at topic level — a single\nhigh-follower author backing up is invisible in aggregate.\nRemaining gap: Need per-author fan-out lag metric to detect\ncelebrity fan-out anomalies before they affect user experience.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b54","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Violated by: Fan-out lag tracked at topic level — a single\nhigh-follower author backing up is invisible in aggregate.\nRemaining gap: Need per-author fan-out lag metric to detect\ncelebrity fan-out anomalies before they affect user experience.","height":70,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b45309","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1856616444,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":518.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":4211,"width":431.0875244140625},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#06b6d4","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b55","backgroundColor":"#c3fae8","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"-JQExSNjd50Okd0lVpWZx","x":-251.5596923828125,"seed":1082615236,"boundElements":[],"y":4272,"opacity":100,"height":150,"width":1530,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":1944769988},{"seed":966659396,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"TQH9VuNk7S2G6AaUJ0IQf","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":18,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Multi-Region — Active-active reads, Active-passive writes","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b56","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Multi-Region — Active-active reads, Active-passive writes","height":22.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#0e7490","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":891902076,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":4280,"width":506.44769287109375},{"seed":947111108,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"w_vtTHSvgf52qhhL_vH9W","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Covered by: Global CDN serves media from nearest edge. API fleet deployed in 3 regions (US-East, EU-West, APAC).\nSocial graph DB: primary in US-East, async replication to EU + APAC (<500ms lag). Feed cache: Redis per-region, populated by\nregional fan-out workers. Kafka: per-region cluster, cross-region replication for global events.\nRTO 30s via Route53 health check + automated DNS failover. RPO <1s via Aurora Global Database sync replication.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b57","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Covered by: Global CDN serves media from nearest edge. API fleet deployed in 3 regions (US-East, EU-West, APAC).\nSocial graph DB: primary in US-East, async replication to EU + APAC (<500ms lag). Feed cache: Redis per-region, populated by\nregional fan-out workers. Kafka: per-region cluster, cross-region replication for global events.\nRTO 30s via Route53 health check + automated DNS failover. RPO <1s via Aurora Global Database sync replication.","height":70,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":252935492,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":4306,"width":861.908935546875},{"seed":1386646596,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"_Zdd4TKTei0eD5rhomiJb","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Violated by: Write routing conflict if two regions both believe they are primary (split-brain during network partition).\nRemaining gap: Write region failover requires human approval for social graph — automated failover risks split-brain.\nCross-region fan-out adds 50-200ms latency for posts by US users to their APAC followers.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b58","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Violated by: Write routing conflict if two regions both believe they are primary (split-brain during network partition).\nRemaining gap: Write region failover requires human approval for social graph — automated failover risks split-brain.\nCross-region fan-out adds 50-200ms latency for posts by US users to their APAC followers.","height":52.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#b45309","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1004595452,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":4371,"width":794.51287841796875},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#4a9eed","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b59","backgroundColor":"#1e1e2e","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"Fq06HhOWI4QPrK10nVQko","x":-251.5596923828125,"seed":974414788,"boundElements":[],"y":4439,"opacity":100,"height":95,"width":1530,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":498808004},{"seed":886786884,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"UwFLyv2GxDYpeOszoyDsq","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":17,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Honest Gaps Summary (production hardening needed):","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b5A","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Honest Gaps Summary (production hardening needed):","height":21.25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#a5d8ff","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":374499708,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":4449,"width":440.5206298828125},{"seed":358171332,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"l8NMJaIKy7CuRwU9V6Vja","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":15,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"1) Cache miss thundering herd: needs request coalescing (mutex\/dog-pile prevention)   2) Redis AOF persistence for like count durability\n3) Cross-region RYOW: social graph writes need session affinity   4) Per-author fan-out lag metric missing   5) Block\/mute filter in celebrity merge path","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b5B","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"1) Cache miss thundering herd: needs request coalescing (mutex\/dog-pile prevention)   2) Redis AOF persistence for like count durability\n3) Cross-region RYOW: social graph writes need session affinity   4) Per-author fan-out lag metric missing   5) Block\/mute filter in celebrity merge path","height":37.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#e5e5e5","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":2105539652,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":4475,"width":1110.9443359375},{"seed":841763396,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"haDicBkUXWExKhRg8919e","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":26,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"NEWS FEED — Step 11: Multi-Region Strategy","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b5C","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"NEWS FEED — Step 11: Multi-Region Strategy","height":32.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":398449148,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":98.4403076171875,"angle":0,"y":4637,"width":586.2216796875},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#4a9eed","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b5D","backgroundColor":"#dbe4ff","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"version":5,"roundness":{"type":3},"type":"rectangle","updated":1772747707441,"id":"576XVPYTcvvc6cNCdbVQq","x":-251.5596923828125,"seed":1580360132,"boundElements":[],"y":4674,"opacity":100,"height":100,"width":1530,"frameId":null,"strokeStyle":"solid","versionNonce":675271620},{"seed":1619626308,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"SkNOy-6yeISTxmfiaS430","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":19,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Core Decision: Active-Active Reads, Active-Passive Writes (per user home region)","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b5E","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Core Decision: Active-Active Reads, Active-Passive Writes (per user home region)","height":23.75,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#2563eb","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1529559676,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":4682,"width":749.43505859375},{"seed":1821360324,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"tgecLVztfgCWY1Z2Ji_4v","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":1,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1772747707441,"locked":false,"text":"Read path: ALL regions serve reads simultaneously from their local Redis + DB replicas. User routed to nearest region. Zero cross-region latency on reads.\nWrite path: Each user has a 'home region' (set at signup). Social graph writes (follow\/unfollow) go to that region's primary ONLY. Avoids distributed transaction complexity.\nWhy not full active-active writes? Follow\/unfollow needs RYOW consistency. Full active-active would require cross-region consensus (Paxos\/Raft) — 200-400ms latency penalty, not worth it.","version":5,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"b5F","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"Read path: ALL regions serve reads simultaneously from their local Redis + DB replicas. User routed to nearest region. Zero cross-region latency on reads.\nWrite path: Each user has a 'home region' (set at signup). Social graph writes (follow\/unfollow) go to that region's primary ONLY. Avoids distributed transaction complexity.\nWhy not full active-active writes? Follow\/unfollow needs RYOW consistency. Full active-active would require cross-region consensus (Paxos\/Raft) — 200-400ms latency penalty, not worth it.","height":52.5,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":739818308,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":5,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":-241.5596923828125,"angle":0,"y":4709,"width":1303.3563232421875},{"isDeleted":false,"locked":false,"strokeColor":"#adb5bd","link":null,"roughness":1,"groupIds":[],"index":"b5G","backgroundColor":"#f8f9fa","angle":0,"fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidt