nHot post = write hotspot on single DB partition.\",\"fontSize\":13,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"User adds comment; visible to all viewers.\\nExample: hot post gets 10K comments in 5 min\\n— thread must stay ordered and paginated.\\nHidden: threaded replies need recursive model.\\nHot post = write hotspot on single DB partition.\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s2r7\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":10,\"y\":1174,\"width\":502,\"height\":178,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#fbbf24\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#fffbeb\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"ao\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":47364464,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":673235344,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s2r7t\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":24,\"y\":1186,\"width\":273.704833984375,\"height\":18.75,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#b45309\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"ap\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":1407440272,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":2020728688,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"FR7 — Real-time Feed Updates  [P1]\",\"fontSize\":15,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"FR7 — Real-time Feed Updates  [P1]\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s2r7b\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":24,\"y\":1210,\"width\":315.75665283203125,\"height\":81.25,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#334155\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"aq\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":756681584,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":1739722640,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"New posts appear without manual refresh.\\nExample: friend posts photo — slides into your\\nfeed within 3 seconds, no page reload needed.\\nHidden: millions of persistent WS\/SSE connections\\nare costly. Push all vs ping-then-pull tradeoff.\",\"fontSize\":13,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"New posts appear without manual refresh.\\nExample: friend posts photo — slides into your\\nfeed within 3 seconds, no page reload needed.\\nHidden: millions of persistent WS\/SSE connections\\nare costly. Push all vs ping-then-pull tradeoff.\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s2r8\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":530,\"y\":1174,\"width\":502,\"height\":178,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#fbbf24\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#fffbeb\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"ar\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":1374856080,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":803500400,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s2r8t\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":544,\"y\":1186,\"width\":195.869873046875,\"height\":18.75,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#b45309\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"as\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":1990663536,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":65641872,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"FR8 — Feed Ranking  [P1]\",\"fontSize\":15,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"contain