"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b4t\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":1155640208,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":906226032,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s11fot\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":24,\"y\":9743,\"width\":287.1748046875,\"height\":18.75,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#b91c1c\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b4u\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":873239920,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":194880912,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Failover Sequence: US-East Goes Down\",\"fontSize\":15,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Failover Sequence: US-East Goes Down\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s11fob\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":24,\"y\":9767,\"width\":367.860595703125,\"height\":162.5,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#334155\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b4v\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":1355135376,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":1118124912,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"T+0s:   US-East API fleet stops responding\\nT+10s:  Route53 health checks fail (2x5s interval)\\nT+30s:  DNS TTL expires — traffic reroutes to EU-West\\nT+31s:  Aurora Global promotes EU-West replica (<1s)\\nT+35s:  Social graph writes now accepted in EU-West\\nT+60s:  Ops paged — incident declared\\nT+4h:   US-East restored, resyncs from EU-West\\n\\nRPO: <1s  (Aurora Global sync replication to EU-West)\\nRTO: ~30s (DNS propagation + Aurora promote)\",\"fontSize\":13,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"T+0s:   US-East API fleet stops responding\\nT+10s:  Route53 health checks fail (2x5s interval)\\nT+30s:  DNS TTL expires — traffic reroutes to EU-West\\nT+31s:  Aurora Global promotes EU-West replica (<1s)\\nT+35s:  Social graph writes now accepted in EU-West\\nT+60s:  Ops paged — incident declared\\nT+4h:   US-East restored, resyncs from EU-West\\n\\nRPO: <1s  (Aurora Global sync replication to EU-West)\\nRTO: ~30s (DNS propagation + Aurora promote)\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s11sov\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":782,\"y\":9731,\"width\":788,\"height\":200,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#a78bfa\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#f5f3ff\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b4w\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":1387816816,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":301101968,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s11sovt\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":796,\"y\":9743,\"width\":223.45489501953125,\"height\":18.75,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#6d28d9\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b4x\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":553125776,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":323767664,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Data Sovereignty + Compliance\",\"fontSize\":15,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Data Sovereignty + Compliance\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s11sovb\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":796,\"y\":9767,\"width\":375.34857177734375,\"height\":195,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#334155\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b4y\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":270137712,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":1350402448,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"GDPR (EU): EU user posts, social graph, profile data must\\nreside in EU-West ONLY. No replication to US or APAC.\\nImplementation: user_home_region field on user record.\\nReplication topology respects regional boundaries.\\n\\nIndia \/ APAC: some countries require local storage.\\nAPAC region stores local user data locally.\\n\\nCross-region fan-out: shares post_id + CDN URL only.\\nNever replicates PII content. CDN serves from home S3.\\n\\nChina: completely separate deployment — out of scope.\",\"fontSize\":13,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"GDPR (EU): EU user posts, social graph, profile data must\\nreside in EU-West ONLY. No replication to US or APAC.\\nImplementation: user_home_region field on user record.\\nReplication topology respects regional boundaries.\\n\\nIndia \/ APAC: some countries require local storage.\\nAPAC region stores local user data locally.\\n\\nCross-region fan-out: shares post_id + CDN URL only.\\nNever replicates PII content. CDN serves from home S3.\\n\\nChina: completely separate deployment — out of scope.\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s11sum\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":10,\"y\":9941,\"width\":1560,\"height\":50,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#134e4a\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#134e4a\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b4z\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":296785296,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":557916016,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s11sumt\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":24,\"y\":9954,\"width\":1122.8541259765625,\"height\":17.5,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#f0fdf4\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b50\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":259607408,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":1719062416,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Active-active reads \/ active-passive writes  |  RTO 30s  |  RPO <1s  |  GDPR: EU data physically isolated  |  Fan-out cross-region shares only post_id + CDN URL\",\"fontSize\":14,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Active-active reads \/ active-passive writes  |  RTO 30s  |  RPO <1s  |  GDPR: EU data physically isolated  |  Fan-out cross-region shares only post_id + CDN URL\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s12bg\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":10,\"y\":10050,\"width\":1560,\"height\":1210,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#cbd5e1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#f8fafc\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b51\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":2093724016,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":884010265,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728299,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s12hd\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":10,\"y\":10050,\"width\":1560,\"height\":46,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#78350f\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#78350f\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b52\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":1276534160,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":1559416055,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728299,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s12tt\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":420,\"y\":10063,\"width\":349.6078186035156,\"height\":26.25,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#fef3c7\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b53\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":1832125296,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":975561209,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728299,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"STEP 12  —  Trade-off Decisions\",\"fontSize\":21,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"STEP 12  —  Trade-off Decisions\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s12sub\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":420,\"y\":10098,\"width\":449.1053466796875,\"height\":17.5,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#64748b\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b54\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":848571280,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":1293686295,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728299,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Format: Decision | Over | Because (3 reasons) | Costs | Revisit if\",\"fontSize\":14,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Format: Decision | Over | Because (3 reasons) | Costs | Revisit if\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s12t1\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":10,\"y\":10116,\"width\":754,\"height\":218,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#3b82f6\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#dbeafe\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b55\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":281154928,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":854145753,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728299,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s12t1t\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":24,\"y\":10128,\"width\":519.2593994140625,\"height\":17.5,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#1d4ed8\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b56\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":1680357776,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":931085111,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728299,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Decision 1 — Posts DB: PostgreSQL (sharded)  over Cassandra \/ MongoDB\",\"fontSize\":14,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Decision 1 — Posts DB: PostgreSQL (sharded)  over Cassandra \/ MongoDB\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s12t1b\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":24,\"y\":10152,\"width\":467.531494140625,\"height\":162.5,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#334155\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b57\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":2092820336,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":1871607737,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Because:\\n1. Cache-miss query: WHERE author_id IN (...) AND created_at > X\\n   Cassandra forces one table per query pattern — too rigid.\\n2. Post schema is well-defined and relational. No flexible-schema benefit.\\n3. Sharded PG gives horizontal scale PLUS full SQL query expressiveness.\\n\\nCosts: Cross-shard queries impossible (app-layer aggregation required).\\nSchema migrations on sharded PG are operationally painful.\\n\\nRevisit if: post schema becomes truly dynamic, or writes exceed 50K\/sec.\",\"fontSize\":13,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Because:\\n1. Cache-miss query: WHERE author_id IN (...) AND created_at > X\\n   Cassandra forces one table per query pattern — too rigid.\\n2. Post schema is well-defined and relational. No flexible-schema benefit.\\n3. Sharded PG gives horizontal scale PLUS full SQL query expressiveness.\\n\\nCosts: Cross-shard queries impossible (app-layer aggregation required).\\nSchema migrations on sharded PG are operationally painful.\\n\\nRevisit if: post schema becomes truly dynamic, or writes exceed 50K\/sec.\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s12t2\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":782,\"y\":10116,\"width\":788,\"height\":218,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#eab308\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#fef9c3\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b58\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":604669840,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":1887485015,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s12t2t\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":796,\"y\":10128,\"width\":441.1954345703125,\"height\":17.5,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#713f12\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b59\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":1567586672,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":1647909017,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Decision 2 — Social Graph: Cassandra  over PostgreSQL \/ Neo4j\",\"fontSize\":14,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Decision 2 — Social Graph: Cassandra  over PostgreSQL \/ Neo4j\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s12t2b\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":796,\"y\":10152,\"width\":455.75341796875,\"height\":162.5,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#334155\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5A\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":242423184,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":1274354039,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Because:\\n1. Only query ever run: get all followees for user X. Cassandra wide-row\\n   (partition=follower_id, cols=followees) is a single partition read, O(1).\\n2. Write throughput: follow\/unfollow events at scale. LSM tree handles\\n   write-heavy workloads natively. PG B-tree struggles here.\\n3. Horizontal scale: add nodes, ranges rebalance automatically.\\n\\nCosts: Eventual consistency by default. No ad-hoc queries.\\n\\nRevisit if: friend-of-friend recommendations needed (Neo4j better).\",\"fontSize\":13,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Because:\\n1. Only query ever run: get all followees for user X. Cassandra wide-row\\n   (partition=follower_id, cols=followees) is a single partition read, O(1).\\n2. Write throughput: follow\/unfollow events at scale. LSM tree handles\\n   write-heavy workloads natively. PG B-tree struggles here.\\n3. Horizontal scale: add nodes, ranges rebalance automatically.\\n\\nCosts: Eventual consistency by default. No ad-hoc queries.\\n\\nRevisit if: friend-of-friend recommendations needed (Neo4j better).\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s12t3\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":10,\"y\":10344,\"width\":754,\"height\":218,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#ef4444\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#fee2e2\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5B\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":371116912,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":1822203257,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s12t3t\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":24,\"y\":10356,\"width\":447.9715270996094,\"height\":17.5,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#b91c1c\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5C\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":2023351184,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":790680215,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Decision 3 — Async Fan-out: Kafka  over RabbitMQ \/ SQS \/ sync\",\"fontSize\":14,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Decision 3 — Async Fan-out: Kafka  over RabbitMQ \/ SQS \/ sync\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s12t3b\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":24,\"y\":10380,\"width\":468.7403564453125,\"height\":178.75,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#334155\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5D\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":1628691824,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":1845266009,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Because:\\n1. Replay: Kafka retains messages — crashed worker catches up from\\n   exact offset. RabbitMQ deletes on ACK. No replay possible.\\n2. Throughput: Kafka handles 69 MB\/s fan-out + 46 MB\/s likes easily.\\n   RabbitMQ struggles above ~50K msg\/sec without significant tuning.\\n3. Consumer groups: adding fan-out workers needs zero producer changes.\\n\\nCosts: Operational complexity — KRaft, rebalancing, lag monitoring.\\nAt-least-once delivery needs idempotent consumers (ZADD NX).\\n\\nRevisit if: fan-out volume drops below 1K posts\/sec — use SQS instead.\",\"fontSize\":13,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Because:\\n1. Replay: Kafka retains messages — crashed worker catches up from\\n   exact offset. RabbitMQ deletes on ACK. No replay possible.\\n2. Throughput: Kafka handles 69 MB\/s fan-out + 46 MB\/s likes easily.\\n   RabbitMQ struggles above ~50K msg\/sec without significant tuning.\\n3. Consumer groups: adding fan-out workers needs zero producer changes.\\n\\nCosts: Operational complexity — KRaft, rebalancing, lag monitoring.\\nAt-least-once delivery needs idempotent consumers (ZADD NX).\\n\\nRevisit if: fan-out volume drops below 1K posts\/sec — use SQS instead.\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s12t4\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":782,\"y\":10344,\"width\":788,\"height\":218,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#ec4899\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#fce7f3\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5E\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":1354166672,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":1656252343,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s12t4t\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":796,\"y\":10356,\"width\":497.5593566894531,\"height\":17.5,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#9d174d\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5F\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":1872146288,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":288117561,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Decision 4 — Feed Cache: Redis Sorted Set  over Memcached \/ Mat.View\",\"fontSize\":14,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Decision 4 — Feed Cache: Redis Sorted Set  over Memcached \/ Mat.View\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s12t4b\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":796,\"y\":10380,\"width\":487.564453125,\"height\":195,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#334155\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5G\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":2114076560,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":618682583,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Because:\\n1. Native sorted structure: ZREVRANGEBYSCORE gives stable cursor-based\\n   pagination natively. No equivalent in Memcached.\\n2. Atomic ops: ZADD + ZRANGE are single-command atomic.\\n   No race conditions between feed write and read.\\n3. Latency: Redis P99 ~1ms. Materialized view needs DB round trip\\n   (20-50ms) and expensive refresh on every post write.\\n\\nCosts: Memory-only (35GB — manageable but real cost).\\nEviction causes thundering herd DB fallback.\\n\\nRevisit if: feed cache grows beyond 500GB — consider tiered storage.\",\"fontSize\":13,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Because:\\n1. Native sorted structure: ZREVRANGEBYSCORE gives stable cursor-based\\n   pagination natively. No equivalent in Memcached.\\n2. Atomic ops: ZADD + ZRANGE are single-command atomic.\\n   No race conditions between feed write and read.\\n3. Latency: Redis P99 ~1ms. Materialized view needs DB round trip\\n   (20-50ms) and expensive refresh on every post write.\\n\\nCosts: Memory-only (35GB — manageable but real cost).\\nEviction causes thundering herd DB fallback.\\n\\nRevisit if: feed cache grows beyond 500GB — consider tiered storage.\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s12t5\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":10,\"y\":10572,\"width\":754,\"height\":208,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#22c55e\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#dcfce7\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5H\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":166674800,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":1519354905,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s12t5t\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":24,\"y\":10584,\"width\":398.6915283203125,\"height\":17.5,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#15803d\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5I\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":1085525392,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":2066556407,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Decision 5 — Consistency: Eventual for Feed  over Strong\",\"fontSize\":14,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Decision 5 — Consistency: Eventual for Feed  over Strong\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s12t5b\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":24,\"y\":10608,\"width\":442.16851806640625,\"height\":195,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#334155\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5J\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":795186032,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":1981389049,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Because:\\n1. User tolerance: seeing a post 2-5s late is invisible to users.\\n   Seeing 400ms write latency on every post is very visible.\\n2. Cross-region strong consistency costs 200-400ms (network RTT)\\n   on every post create — violates P99 <1s write SLO.\\n3. Throughput: sync cross-region replication serializes all writes,\\n   limiting throughput to slowest region's ACK time.\\n\\nCosts: slight ordering differences across devices, RYOW exception\\nneeded for follow\/unfollow.\\n\\nRevisit if: financial or legal compliance content added to feed.\",\"fontSize\":13,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Because:\\n1. User tolerance: seeing a post 2-5s late is invisible to users.\\n   Seeing 400ms write latency on every post is very visible.\\n2. Cross-region strong consistency costs 200-400ms (network RTT)\\n   on every post create — violates P99 <1s write SLO.\\n3. Throughput: sync cross-region replication serializes all writes,\\n   limiting throughput to slowest region's ACK time.\\n\\nCosts: slight ordering differences across devices, RYOW exception\\nneeded for follow\/unfollow.\\n\\nRevisit if: financial or legal compliance content added to feed.\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s12t6\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":782,\"y\":10572,\"width\":788,\"height\":208,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#a78bfa\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#f5f3ff\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5K\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":302226320,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":1151553303,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s12t6t\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":796,\"y\":10584,\"width\":407.9454345703125,\"height\":17.5,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#6d28d9\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5L\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":910271856,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":1162744281,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Decision 6 — Hybrid Fan-out  over Pure Write or Pure Read\",\"fontSize\":14,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Decision 6 — Hybrid Fan-out  over Pure Write or Pure Read\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s12t6b\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":796,\"y\":10608,\"width\":456.9234313964844,\"height\":178.75,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#334155\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5M\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":69839248,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":196564023,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Because:\\n1. Pure write breaks at 10M followers: 10M Redis writes\/post\\n   saturates worker pool, creates 30min Kafka consumer lag spikes.\\n2. Pure read breaks at 232K QPS: every read recomputes merge from\\n   scratch. Twitter abandoned pure pull in 2012 for exactly this reason.\\n3. Hybrid amortizes correctly: 99.9% accounts (<1M followers) get\\n   instant precomputed reads. 0.1% celebrities merge at read time.\\n\\nCosts: two code paths, 1M threshold is a magic number needing tuning.\\n\\nRevisit if: 50%+ users follow >5 celebrities — merge cost dominates.\",\"fontSize\":13,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Because:\\n1. Pure write breaks at 10M followers: 10M Redis writes\/post\\n   saturates worker pool, creates 30min Kafka consumer lag spikes.\\n2. Pure read breaks at 232K QPS: every read recomputes merge from\\n   scratch. Twitter abandoned pure pull in 2012 for exactly this reason.\\n3. Hybrid amortizes correctly: 99.9% accounts (<1M followers) get\\n   instant precomputed reads. 0.1% celebrities merge at read time.\\n\\nCosts: two code paths, 1M threshold is a magic number needing tuning.\\n\\nRevisit if: 50%+ users follow >5 celebrities — merge cost dominates.\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s12t7\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":10,\"y\":10790,\"width\":1560,\"height\":180,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#eab308\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#fef9c3\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5N\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":1808496496,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":759197369,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s12t7t\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":24,\"y\":10802,\"width\":547.38525390625,\"height\":17.5,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#713f12\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5O\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":576583568,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":407745879,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Decision 7 — Retry Strategy: Exponential Backoff + Jitter  over Fixed Interval\",\"fontSize\":14,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Decision 7 — Retry Strategy: Exponential Backoff + Jitter  over Fixed Interval\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s12t7b\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":24,\"y\":10826,\"width\":807.3641357421875,\"height\":146.25,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#334155\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5P\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":877332848,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":613691289,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Because:\\n1. Thundering herd prevention: 150 workers that all hit Kafka timeout simultaneously retry at DIFFERENT times due to jitter.\\n   Desynchronized load instead of synchronized retry storm that re-breaks the recovering service.\\n2. Self-healing: exponential backoff gives recovering services time to stabilize before the next retry wave arrives.\\n3. Formula: min(100ms * 2^attempt + rand(0,100ms), 30000ms) — mathematically proven to converge under Poisson load.\\n\\nCosts: users see higher latency on retry path (up to 30s max backoff). DLQ accumulates faster during extended outages.\\n\\nRevisit if: SLA requires <5s recovery — circuit breaker + immediate failover to backup becomes more appropriate.\",\"fontSize\":13,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Because:\\n1. Thundering herd prevention: 150 workers that all hit Kafka timeout simultaneously retry at DIFFERENT times due to jitter.\\n   Desynchronized load instead of synchronized retry storm that re-breaks the recovering service.\\n2. Self-healing: exponential backoff gives recovering services time to stabilize before the next retry wave arrives.\\n3. Formula: min(100ms * 2^attempt + rand(0,100ms), 30000ms) — mathematically proven to converge under Poisson load.\\n\\nCosts: users see higher latency on retry path (up to 30s max backoff). DLQ accumulates faster during extended outages.\\n\\nRevisit if: SLA requires <5s recovery — circuit breaker + immediate failover to backup becomes more appropriate.\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s12sum\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":10,\"y\":10980,\"width\":1560,\"height\":50,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#78350f\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#78350f\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5Q\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":1356367248,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":1102770807,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s12sumt\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":24,\"y\":10993,\"width\":1351.05419921875,\"height\":17.5,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#fef3c7\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5R\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":721967984,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":24958073,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Posts: PG (query flex)  |  Graph: Cassandra (write throughput)  |  Fan-out: Kafka (replay)  |  Cache: Redis SortedSet (cursors)  |  Consistency: Eventual (speed)  |  Fan-out: Hybrid  |  Retry: Jitter\",\"fontSize\":14,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Posts: PG (query flex)  |  Graph: Cassandra (write throughput)  |  Fan-out: Kafka (replay)  |  Cache: Redis SortedSet (cursors)  |  Consistency: Eventual (speed)  |  Fan-out: Hybrid  |  Retry: Jitter\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s13bg\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":10,\"y\":11100,\"width\":1560,\"height\":870,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#cbd5e1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#f8fafc\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5S\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":751915920,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":12815255,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s13hd\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":10,\"y\":11100,\"width\":1560,\"height\":46,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#1e3a5f\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#1e3a5f\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5T\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":1112239472,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":129883481,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s13tt\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":450,\"y\":11113,\"width\":338.60382080078125,\"height\":26.25,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#f1f5f9\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5U\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":1820352912,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":1100742839,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"STEP 13  —  Interview Strategy\",\"fontSize\":21,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"STEP 13  —  Interview Strategy\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s13sum\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":10,\"y\":11156,\"width\":1560,\"height\":110,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#93c5fd\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#eff6ff\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5V\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":1666989936,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":917162553,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s13sumt\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":24,\"y\":11168,\"width\":425.81976318359375,\"height\":18.75,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#1d4ed8\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5W\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":1058910096,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":1978192343,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"30-Second Verbal Summary  (practice saying this out loud)\",\"fontSize\":15,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"30-Second Verbal Summary  (practice saying this out loud)\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s13sumb\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":24,\"y\":11192,\"width\":1042.3780517578125,\"height\":65,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#334155\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5X\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":243454320,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":1462180633,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"\\\"A News Feed aggregates posts from N followed accounts into a personalized ranked stream. The core challenge is fan-out — a celebrity with 10M followers posting\\nonce creates 10M feed-cache update events. We solve this with a hybrid approach: fan-out-on-write via Kafka workers for normal users,\\nfan-out-on-read at merge time for celebrity accounts. Feeds are stored as Redis sorted sets, serving reads in under 5ms. Like counters use Redis INCR\\nwith async DB flush every 30 seconds. The system shards posts by user_id, uses Cassandra for the social graph, and runs active-active reads across 3 regions.\\\"\",\"fontSize\":13,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"\\\"A News Feed aggregates posts from N followed accounts into a personalized ranked stream. The core challenge is fan-out — a celebrity with 10M followers posting\\nonce creates 10M feed-cache update events. We solve this with a hybrid approach: fan-out-on-write via Kafka workers for normal users,\\nfan-out-on-read at merge time for celebrity accounts. Feeds are stored as Redis sorted sets, serving reads in under 5ms. Like counters use Redis INCR\\nwith async DB flush every 30 seconds. The system shards posts by user_id, uses Cassandra for the social graph, and runs active-active reads across 3 regions.\\\"\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s13q\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":10,\"y\":11276,\"width\":1560,\"height\":295,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#fca5a5\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#fff1f2\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5Y\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":752958864,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":1723760375,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s13qt\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":24,\"y\":11288,\"width\":304.81475830078125,\"height\":18.75,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#b91c1c\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5Z\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":2064065392,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":1235636217,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"3 Hardest Interview Questions + Answers\",\"fontSize\":15,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"3 Hardest Interview Questions + Answers\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s13q1\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":24,\"y\":11312,\"width\":490,\"height\":245,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#fca5a5\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5a\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":1996688272,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":1184991255,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s13q1t\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":38,\"y\":11324,\"width\":206.82974243164062,\"height\":32.5,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#b91c1c\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5b\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":925971824,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":338421977,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Q: How do you handle a celebrity\\nwith 100M followers posting?\",\"fontSize\":13,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Q: How do you handle a celebrity\\nwith 100M followers posting?\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s13q1b\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":38,\"y\":11358,\"width\":275.20965576171875,\"height\":146.25,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#334155\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5c\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":2008750480,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":59141431,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"A: Hybrid fan-out. Do NOT push to 100M\\nRedis caches at write time — worker queue\\nwould saturate for 30+ minutes.\\nInstead: store in celebrity_posts table.\\nAt read time: ZRANGE precomputed feed +\\nSELECT celebrity_posts WHERE author IN\\n(followed celebrities) LIMIT 20.\\nMerge both result sets by ranking score.\\nAdd ~20ms to read latency. Fully worth it.\",\"fontSize\":13,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"A: Hybrid fan-out. Do NOT push to 100M\\nRedis caches at write time — worker queue\\nwould saturate for 30+ minutes.\\nInstead: store in celebrity_posts table.\\nAt read time: ZRANGE precomputed feed +\\nSELECT celebrity_posts WHERE author IN\\n(followed celebrities) LIMIT 20.\\nMerge both result sets by ranking score.\\nAdd ~20ms to read latency. Fully worth it.\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s13q2\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":532,\"y\":11312,\"width\":490,\"height\":245,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#fca5a5\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5d\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":1212745584,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":810247609,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s13q2t\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":546,\"y\":11324,\"width\":220.58375549316406,\"height\":32.5,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#b91c1c\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5e\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":37840784,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":1490136663,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Q: How do you paginate a live feed\\nwithout duplicates or skips?\",\"fontSize\":13,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Q: How do you paginate a live feed\\nwithout duplicates or skips?\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s13q2b\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":546,\"y\":11358,\"width\":254.44874572753906,\"height\":162.5,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#334155\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5f\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":1251383664,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":422069913,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"A: Cursor-based pagination using\\ncursor = base64(ranking_score:post_id).\\nQuery: ZREVRANGEBYSCORE feed:alice\\n(cursor_score -inf LIMIT 0 20.\\nFetch posts BELOW the cursor score.\\nThis is stable — new posts inserted at\\nthe top never shift existing positions.\\nOffset-based (LIMIT 20 OFFSET 100)\\nbreaks because new insertions shift\\nall offsets downward.\",\"fontSize\":13,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"A: Cursor-based pagination using\\ncursor = base64(ranking_score:post_id).\\nQuery: ZREVRANGEBYSCORE feed:alice\\n(cursor_score -inf LIMIT 0 20.\\nFetch posts BELOW the cursor score.\\nThis is stable — new posts inserted at\\nthe top never shift existing positions.\\nOffset-based (LIMIT 20 OFFSET 100)\\nbreaks because new insertions shift\\nall offsets downward.\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s13q3\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":1058,\"y\":11312,\"width\":498,\"height\":245,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#fca5a5\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#ffffff\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5g\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":1120794000,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":559401847,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s13q3t\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":1072,\"y\":11324,\"width\":255.2677001953125,\"height\":32.5,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#b91c1c\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5h\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":291629936,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":427166585,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Q: A viral post gets 500K likes in 1 hour\\n— how does the system handle it?\",\"fontSize\":13,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Q: A viral post gets 500K likes in 1 hour\\n— how does the system handle it?\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s13q3b\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":1072,\"y\":11358,\"width\":258.01068115234375,\"height\":162.5,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#334155\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5i\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":513328016,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":1767720087,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"A: Redis INCR on like_count:{post_id}.\\nAtomic, handles 100K+ ops\/sec per node.\\nLike dedup: SADD liked_by:{post_id}.\\nReturns 0 if already liked — idempotent.\\nNo DB write on the critical path.\\nAsync flusher batches to DB every 30s\\n(single UPDATE per post, not per like).\\nIf post crosses 10M likes, switch to\\nHyperLogLog (12KB, 0.81% error).\\nCount is eventually consistent — fine.\",\"fontSize\":13,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"A: Redis INCR on like_count:{post_id}.\\nAtomic, handles 100K+ ops\/sec per node.\\nLike dedup: SADD liked_by:{post_id}.\\nReturns 0 if already liked — idempotent.\\nNo DB write on the critical path.\\nAsync flusher batches to DB every 30s\\n(single UPDATE per post, not per like).\\nIf post crosses 10M likes, switch to\\nHyperLogLog (12KB, 0.81% error).\\nCount is eventually consistent — fine.\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s13miss\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":10,\"y\":11581,\"width\":754,\"height\":175,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#fcd34d\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#fffbeb\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5j\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":1190329712,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":1501049945,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s13misst\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":24,\"y\":11593,\"width\":204.50987243652344,\"height\":18.75,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#b45309\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5k\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":333042064,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":1083611575,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"What Most Candidates Miss\",\"fontSize\":15,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"What Most Candidates Miss\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s13missb\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":24,\"y\":11617,\"width\":461.1485290527344,\"height\":97.5,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#334155\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5l\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":210882416,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":755122489,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"1. Cursor pagination — everyone says OFFSET. Wrong on live feeds.\\n2. BN7 workload isolation — viral post like-spike starves feed reads.\\n3. Idempotency on retry — duplicate posts without dedup keys.\\n4. Media pending state — broken feed thumbnails before transcoding.\\n5. Mute\/block must apply in the celebrity merge path too.\\n6. RYOW consistency for follow\/unfollow (not just eventual everywhere).\",\"fontSize\":13,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"1. Cursor pagination — everyone says OFFSET. Wrong on live feeds.\\n2. BN7 workload isolation — viral post like-spike starves feed reads.\\n3. Idempotency on retry — duplicate posts without dedup keys.\\n4. Media pending state — broken feed thumbnails before transcoding.\\n5. Mute\/block must apply in the celebrity merge path too.\\n6. RYOW consistency for follow\/unfollow (not just eventual everywhere).\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s13diff\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":782,\"y\":11581,\"width\":788,\"height\":175,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#a78bfa\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#f5f3ff\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5m\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":432611216,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":1277709015,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s13difft\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":796,\"y\":11593,\"width\":168.7498779296875,\"height\":18.75,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#6d28d9\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5n\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":445014384,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":561492505,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Senior vs Staff Answer\",\"fontSize\":15,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Senior vs Staff Answer\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s13diffb\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":796,\"y\":11617,\"width\":516.4635009765625,\"height\":113.75,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#334155\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5o\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":10399120,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":413587447,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Senior: adds Redis cache, Kafka fan-out, mentions hybrid fan-out.\\nStaff:\\n  Quantifies every tradeoff with specific thresholds (1M follower boundary).\\n  States exact retry formula with jitter and explains WHY jitter prevents storms.\\n  Identifies honest production gaps (thundering herd, per-author lag metrics).\\n  Walks through the exact failover sequence with real timing numbers.\\n  Notes GDPR boundary — EU data cannot replicate to US, ever.\",\"fontSize\":13,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Senior: adds Redis cache, Kafka fan-out, mentions hybrid fan-out.\\nStaff:\\n  Quantifies every tradeoff with specific thresholds (1M follower boundary).\\n  States exact retry formula with jitter and explains WHY jitter prevents storms.\\n  Identifies honest production gaps (thundering herd, per-author lag metrics).\\n  Walks through the exact failover sequence with real timing numbers.\\n  Notes GDPR boundary — EU data cannot replicate to US, ever.\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s13nums\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":10,\"y\":11766,\"width\":1560,\"height\":80,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#1e3a5f\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#1e3a5f\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5p\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":1612231536,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":1271662329,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s13numst\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":24,\"y\":11778,\"width\":187.4698486328125,\"height\":18.75,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#93c5fd\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5q\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":1368554384,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":739688727,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Key Numbers to Memorize:\",\"fontSize\":15,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Key Numbers to Memorize:\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s13numsv\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":24,\"y\":11802,\"width\":1344.06787109375,\"height\":17.5,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#f1f5f9\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b5r\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":596690288,\"version\":3,\"versionNonce\":1451409369,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748728300,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"232K peak feed read QPS  |  3.2 GB\/s outbound BW  |  35 GB feed cache  |  69 MB\/s Kafka fan-out  |  Feed P99 < 500ms  |  RTO 30s  |  RPO < 1s  |  Fan-out lag < 5s  |  Like flush every 30s\",\"fontSize\":14,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"232K peak feed read QPS  |  3.2 GB\/s outbound BW  |  35 GB feed cache  |  69 MB\/s Kafka fan-out  |  Feed P99 < 500ms  |  RTO 30s  |  RPO < 1s  |  Fan-out lag < 5s  |  Like flush every 30s\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25}],\"files\":{}}","version":3,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","index":"bDe","roundness":null,"containerId":null,"originalText":"{\"type\":\"excalidraw\/clipboard\",\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"s1bg\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":10,\"y\":10,\"width\":1560,\"height\":680,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#cbd5e1\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#f8fafc\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"a0\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":1321236336,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":942105488,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s1hd\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":10,\"y\":10,\"width\":1560,\"height\":46,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#1e3a5f\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#1e3a5f\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"a1\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":1429796752,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":1260281200,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s1tt\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":490,\"y\":23,\"width\":413.53173828125,\"height\":26.25,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#f1f5f9\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"a2\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":1889536368,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":1117024656,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"STEP 1  —  Problem Framing: News Feed\",\"fontSize\":21,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"STEP 1  —  Problem Framing: News Feed\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s1a\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":10,\"y\":66,\"width\":490,\"height\":222,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#93c5fd\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#eff6ff\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"a3\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":1884521872,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":877735792,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s1at\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":24,\"y\":78,\"width\":99.96791076660156,\"height\":20,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#1d4ed8\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"a4\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":347954032,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":1479524240,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Core Problem\",\"fontSize\":16,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Core Problem\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s1ab\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":24,\"y\":103,\"width\":329.51763916015625,\"height\":157.5,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#334155\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"a5\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":619467664,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":1398391152,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Aggregates posts from all followed accounts\\ninto one personalized ranked stream.\\n\\nWithout it: users visit each profile manually.\\nThis is how social networks worked pre-2006.\\n\\nCentral tension: 1 celebrity post triggers\\n10M feed-cache updates — the fan-out problem.\\nEvery design decision traces back to this.\",\"fontSize\":14,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Aggregates posts from all followed accounts\\ninto one personalized ranked stream.\\n\\nWithout it: users visit each profile manually.\\nThis is how social networks worked pre-2006.\\n\\nCentral tension: 1 celebrity post triggers\\n10M feed-cache updates — the fan-out problem.\\nEvery design decision traces back to this.\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s1b\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":518,\"y\":66,\"width\":490,\"height\":222,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#86efac\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#f0fdf4\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"a6\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":761294192,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":2033274256,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s1bt\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":532,\"y\":78,\"width\":128.28790283203125,\"height\":20,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#15803d\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"a7\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":691757456,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":1736446832,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"User Archetypes\",\"fontSize\":16,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"User Archetypes\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s1bb\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":532,\"y\":103,\"width\":303.22564697265625,\"height\":175,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#334155\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"a8\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":600915824,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":1590762384,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"PRODUCERS — celebrities, brands, creators\\n  Post rarely. Millions of followers.\\n  Create massive fan-out per write.\\n\\nCONSUMERS — regular users\\n  Read 10x per day. Few followers.\\n  Low fan-out writes, high read volume.\\n\\nRead : Write = 100 : 1\\nThis single ratio drives the architecture.\",\"fontSize\":14,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"PRODUCERS — celebrities, brands, creators\\n  Post rarely. Millions of followers.\\n  Create massive fan-out per write.\\n\\nCONSUMERS — regular users\\n  Read 10x per day. Few followers.\\n  Low fan-out writes, high read volume.\\n\\nRead : Write = 100 : 1\\nThis single ratio drives the architecture.\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s1c\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":1026,\"y\":66,\"width\":544,\"height\":222,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#d8b4fe\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#fdf4ff\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"a9\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":746106768,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":118236528,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s1ct\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":1040,\"y\":78,\"width\":262.83172607421875,\"height\":20,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#7e22ce\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"aA\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":2019021168,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":1531390352,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Operations + Real-World Examples\",\"fontSize\":16,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Operations + Real-World Examples\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s1cb\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":1040,\"y\":103,\"width\":333.9695739746094,\"height\":140,\"angle\"