:  10B \/ 86,400 = 115,740  ~ 116K QPS\\n\\nPeak QPS  (x4 — evening prime-time spike):\\n  Feed reads:  232K QPS  |  Writes: 2.3K QPS  |  Likes: 464K QPS\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s4rw\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":778,\"y\":2558,\"width\":792,\"height\":175,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#fca5a5\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#fff1f2\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b0q\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":2111895920,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":1902543248,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s4rwt\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":792,\"y\":2570,\"width\":151.2958526611328,\"height\":20,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#b91c1c\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b0r\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":131700112,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":526917488,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Read \/ Write Ratio\",\"fontSize\":16,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Read \/ Write Ratio\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s4rwb\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":792,\"y\":2595,\"width\":357.1116638183594,\"height\":140,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#334155\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b0s\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":744508272,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":37736336,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"58K reads QPS \/ 580 write QPS  =  100 : 1\\n\\nWhy? Users consume far more than they create.\\nEven active users post once a week but open\\nthe feed 10+ times daily.\\n\\nThis ratio drives the core design principle:\\nOPTIMISE AGGRESSIVELY FOR THE READ PATH.\",\"fontSize\":14,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"58K reads QPS \/ 580 write QPS  =  100 : 1\\n\\nWhy? Users consume far more than they create.\\nEven active users post once a week but open\\nthe feed 10+ times daily.\\n\\nThis ratio drives the core design principle:\\nOPTIMISE AGGRESSIVELY FOR THE READ PATH.\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s4stor\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":10,\"y\":2745,\"width\":750,\"height\":268,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#93c5fd\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#eff6ff\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b0t\",\"roundness\":{\"type\":3},\"seed\":19948432,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":504541552,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false},{\"id\":\"s4stort\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":24,\"y\":2757,\"width\":299.3917236328125,\"height\":20,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#1d4ed8\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b0u\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":858086768,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":113204624,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Storage Per Record  +  Total Storage\",\"fontSize\":16,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Storage Per Record  +  Total Storage\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s4storb\",\"type\":\"text\",\"x\":24,\"y\":2782,\"width\":421.589599609375,\"height\":243.75,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#334155\",\"backgroundColor\":\"transparent\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":2,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\":[],\"frameId\":null,\"index\":\"b0v\",\"roundness\":null,\"seed\":41775504,\"version\":2,\"versionNonce\":1302004592,\"isDeleted\":false,\"boundElements\":[],\"updated\":1772748707483,\"link\":null,\"locked\":false,\"text\":\"Post row:\\n  post_id(8) + user_id(8) + content(500)\\n  + media_url(100) + created_at(8)\\n  + like_count(8) + metadata(200)  =  ~850B ~ 1KB\\n\\nFeed cache (Redis sorted set per user):\\n  20 post_ids(160) + 20 scores(160) + meta(30) = 350B\\n\\nSocial graph edge:  follower_id(8)+followee_id(8)+ts(8) = 24B\\n\\nTotal (with 3x replication):\\n  Posts:      50M\/day x 1KB x 365 x 3  =  55 TB\/yr\\n  Media:      50M x 30% x 500KB x 3    =  22 TB\/DAY  → S3\\n  Soc.Graph:  500M x 300 x 24B x 3     =  11 TB total\\n  Feed cache: 100M active users x 350B  =  35 GB  ← fits Redis!\",\"fontSize\":13,\"fontFamily\":5,\"textAlign\":\"left\",\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"containerId\":null,\"originalText\":\"Post row:\\n  post_id(8) + user_id(8) + content(500)\\n  + media_url(100) + created_at(8)\\n  + like_count(8) + metadata(200)  =  ~850B ~ 1KB\\n\\nFeed cache (Redis sorted set per user):\\n  20 post_ids(160) + 20 scores(160) + meta(30) = 350B\\n\\nSocial graph edge:  follower_id(8)+followee_id(8)+ts(8) = 24B\\n\\nTotal (with 3x replication):\\n  Posts:      50M\/day x 1KB x 365 x 3  =  55 TB\/yr\\n  Media:      50M x 30% x 500KB x 3    =  22 TB\/DAY  → S3\\n  Soc.Graph:  500M x 300 x 24B x 3     =  11 TB total\\n  Feed cache: 100M active users x 350B  =  35 GB  ← fits Redis!\",\"autoResize\":true,\"lineHeight\":1.25},{\"id\":\"s4bw\",\"type\":\"rectangle\",\"x\":778,\"y\":2745,\"width\":792,\"height\":268,\"angle\":0,\"strokeColor\":\"#d8b4fe\",\"backgroundColor\":\"#fdf4ff\",\"fillStyle\":\"solid\",\"strokeWidth\":1,\"strokeStyle\":\"solid\",\"roughness\":1,\"opacity\":100,\"groupIds\"